Umubare w'abanduye coronavirus (COVID-19) wiyongereye cyane mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza, kuva ku ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020
Umubare w'abantu banduye coronavirus (COVID-19) ugaragaza ko hari ibintu byinshi bisa hagati y'ibihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'ibihugu bikorana n'Ubwongereza, byemeza ko nubwo icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiri mu byiciro bitandukanye mu bihugu bitandukanye, kiri kwiyongera ku isi hose ku buryo bwihuse.
Nk'uko byagenze mu Butaliyani, ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibyumba by'indembe bikeneye kwitegura kurushaho kubera umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye ubuvuzi, cyane cyane ubuvuzi bukabije.
Ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, abarwayi ba pneumonia bataramenyekana icyateye basanzwemo mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'Ubushinwa Gishinzwe Kurwanya no Kurinda Indwara cyatangaje ko iki cyorezo cyatewe na virusi ya koronavirusi itagira inkomoko, ubu izwi ku izina rya SARS-CoV-2.
Kuva icyo gihe, icyorezo cyatewe na virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 cyiswe coronavirus disease (COVID-19).
Ubushakashatsi bugaragaza ko hafi 80% by'abantu banduye COVID-19 barwara indwara zidakomeye, harimo indwara y'ubuhumekero cyangwa nta y'ibicurane, kandi abenshi muri bo bakira.
Mu bice bigera kuri 14%, COVID-19 ihinduka indwara ikomeye cyane igomba gufungirwa mu bitaro, mu gihe 6% by'abantu barwara cyane cyane bagakenera ubuvuzi bwihuse.
Abarwayi barwariye mu bitaro kubera COVID-19 bapfa ku kigero cya 4%.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, twasuzumye umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 muri buri gihugu cyo mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi (EU/EEA) no mu Burayi (UK) tugereranya n'icy'Intara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Turagereranya kandi imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 muri EU/EEA na UK n'u Butaliyani mu gihe cyo ku ya 31 Mutarama-15 Werurwe 2020.
Abarwayi ba COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA na UK
Nyuma y'Ubushinwa, COVID-19 yakwirakwiriye mu tundi duce kandi imyitwarire ya COVID-19 yarushijeho kwiyongera mu bindi bice by'isi bikurikiyeho.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo ku isi.
Mu itangazo ry'Eurosurveillance 2020 ryo ku ya 5 Werurwe, Spiteri na bagenzi be bavuze ku barwayi ba mbere ba COVID-19 mu Burayi bakurikije ibisobanuro bya OMS.
Mu karere ka EU/EEA, abarwayi ba mbere bagaragaye mu Bufaransa ku ya 24 Mutarama 2020 ubwo abantu bageraga mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, COVID-19 yari imaze kugaragara mu bihugu 30 byose bigize EU/EEA na UK, aho hagati ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 n'uwo munsi w'icyunamo, hari hari abarwayi 39,768 n'abamaze gupfa 1,727, mu gihe abarwayi 17,750 n'abamaze gupfa 1,441 bari mu Butaliyani gusa.
Kubona umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 n'abandura COVID-19 uko wiyongera
Ikigo cy'u Burayi gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (ECDC), imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 muri buri gihugu ku isi, ituruka ku mbuga za Leta nk'ibiro by'ubuzima, ibigo by'ubuzima bya OMS n'ibiro by'ingendo, iherutse kuvugururwa buri munsi saa mbiri za mu gitondo.
Aya makuru yakoreshejwe mu gusuzuma uko COVID-19 imeze muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, agereranywa n'ibyabaye mu Butaliyani.
Mu rwego rwo kubara umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakirwara, twabaze umubare w'abantu banduye COVID-19 mu minsi 14, muri buri gihugu cya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, mu gihe cy'itariki ya 1 Mutarama-15 Werurwe 2020.
Twerekanye kandi umubare w'abanduye muri buri gihugu wiyongereye ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020 saa mbiri za mu gitondo ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama15 Werurwe.
Imyitwarire ya COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA na UK
Umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 mu minsi 14 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza muri rusange ukurikije uwo mu Ntara ya Hubei (Ubushinwa) (Igishushanyo cya 1).
Muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza muri rusange, imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 yatangiye kwiyongera ahagana ku ya 21 Gashyantare, maze yiyongera cyane ahagana ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020 (Ibisobanuro).
Ibi byatewe n'ubwiyongere bwihuse bw'ibimenyetso biturutse mu Butaliyani, ariko ibindi bihugu byose bya EU/EEA na UK byerekanye ubwiyongere bw'ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 (Ibitangazamakuru).
Igishushanyo cya 2 kigaragaza imibare y'abantu banduye COVID-19, mu bihugu bya EU/EEA na UK ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani mu gihe cyo ku ya 31 Mutarama15 Werurwe 2020.
Igaragaza ko, ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe saa mbiri za mu gitondo, ibihugu 15 bya EU/EEA n'ibindi 15 byo mu Bwongereza byari bifite umubare w'abanduye ungana n'uw'u Butaliyani mu byumweru 3 gusa cyangwa munsi yaho.
Ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi bigaragaza ko umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 wiyongera cyane muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza.
Imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 igaragaza ko iki cyorezo gikomeje kwiyongera ku kigero kimwe mu bihugu byose.
Ibi biracyari uko nubwo ibihugu bifite uburyo butandukanye bwo kwivuza, hashingiwe ku mpamvu zitandukanye zo kumenya niba umuntu arwaye cyangwa se niba afite ibimenyetso bitandukanye byo gupima COVID-19, harimo no kongera umubare w'abantu bapimwa.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu turere twibasiwe n'ibiza mu Butaliyani batangaje ko 10% by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bari bakeneye ubuvuzi bwihariye kandi amakuru avuga ko ibitaro n'ibyumba by'ubuvuzi bwihariye muri utwo turere byari byuzuye.
Umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 barwariye mu bitaro na/cyangwa mu byumba by'indembe biboneka mu bihugu bya EU/EEA ni 6% na 1% gusa (ibipimo ntabwo byatanzwe).
Ahubwo, ibi bigomba gutangwa mu buryo bufite gahunda, hakurikijwe amakuru agaragaza umubare w'abarwayi n'abapfuye.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2010-11 bwagaragaje ko mu Burayi hari itandukaniro rinini hagati y'ibitanda byo mu bitaro bya magirirane n'ibyo mu bitaro bya magirirane, aho mu Budage ibitanda byari 29.2 naho muri Porutugali byari 4.2 ku baturage 100.000.
Ibi bivuze ko hari ibihugu bifite ibitaro byinshi cyangwa bike ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani (ibitanda 12.5 by'indembe ku baturage 100,000 mu 201011).
Ibyago byo kuzura kw'ibigo by'ubuvuzi, bishingiye ku kugereranya umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 barwariye mu bihugu byose bya EU/EEA na UK hamwe n'ikibazo cy'ibitanda by'indwara z'ubuhumekero bukabije birenze 90%, byerekanwe mu cyegeranyo cya gatandatu cya ECDC cyo gusuzuma ibyago bya COVID-19.
Kubera ko abarwayi bakiri mu bice bimwe na bimwe by'ibihugu bya EU/EEA na UK, kandi ibitaro n'ibyumba by'ubuvuzi bwihariye bikorera abaturage mu bice runaka, amakuru y'abarwayi n'ibitanda by'ubuvuzi bwihariye yagombye kuboneka mu buryo bwa Nomenclature of territorial units for statistics 2 (NUTS-2).
Ibyabaye mu Butaliyani n'ibindi bikorwa by'ubucuruzi mu bindi bihugu bigaragaza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 kigenda kizamuka mu buryo bwihuse muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza.
Ku bw'ibyo, ibitaro n'ibyumba by'ubuvuzi bwihariye bigomba kwitegura guhangana n'ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV-2 mu baturage no kwiyongera kw'umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye ubuvuzi, cyane cyane ubuvuzi bwihariye, nk'uko bimeze mu turere tw'u Butaliyani twugarijwe n'icyorezo.
Nkuko byagaragajwe mu bushakashatsi bw'ingamba za ECDC, kwitegura hakiri kare ni ingenzi mu gukumira ikwirakwira rya SARS-COV-2, harimo no kuva ku gukumira ikwirakwira kugera ku kuvura, kubera ko kwiyongera mu buryo bwihuse kw'umubare w'abarwayi byitezwe ku buyobozi bidashobora guha abayobozi n'ibitaro igihe gihagije cyo gutahura, kwemera no gushyira mu bikorwa ingamba zikenewe mu gihe zitashywe mu bikorwa hakiri kare.
Gusuzuma ibibazo hakiri kare bigaragaza uburyo bwo kwivuza bwo guhangana n'iki kibazo.
Hariho impaka nke ku bushobozi ibihugu bifite bwo kongera imbaraga mu kugabanya ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV-2 no kugabanya ibibazo by'ubuvuzi.
Ibi biramutse bitabaye, byitezwe ko serivisi z'ubuvuzi mu bindi bihugu bya EU/EEA zizagerwaho n'ibibazo bitewe n'umubare w'abarwayi wiyongera cyane bakeneye ubuvuzi bwihuse mu minsi cyangwa ibyumweru biri imbere.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus cy'uburwayi bwa Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), gituma indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero (SARS) coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2), cyahitanye abantu barenga 3,000 n'ubwandu bushya burenga 80,000 mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bihugu byo ku isi, bituma haba ibyago bikomeye.
Kimwe na virusi isa na SARS-CoV, yateje SARS mu bantu babarirwa mu bihumbi mu 2003, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kwanduzwa n'imbeba kandi igatanga ibimenyetso bisa n'ibyo.
Icyakora, COVID-19 ntabwo ifite ubukana nk'ubwa SARS kandi nta bantu benshi yahitanye ariko ikwirakwira cyane kandi yibasira abantu bakuze n'abagabo kurusha abakiri bato n'abagore.
Mu gusubiza ibitabo byinshi byasohotse kuri iki cyorezo, uru rupapuro rugamije kwerekana isesengura ryimbitse ry'ubushakashatsi bwakozwe.
Tuzasuzuma ibintu by'ibanze ku birebana n'indwara, impamvu zitera, mikorobe, uburyo bwo gusuzuma indwara, uburyo bwo kuvurwa, uko umuntu yavuga iby'igihe kizaza n'uko yayirinda.
Nubwo hari ibibazo byinshi bikiriho, twizeye ko ubu bushakashatsi buzatuma tumenya neza icyo kibazo cy'uburwayi kandi bukadukuriraho.
Ibirori byo kwizihiza umwaka wa 2020 ku ya 25 Mutarama byabaye umunsi utazibagirana ku Bashinwa basabwe kuguma mu ngo zabo mu gihe cy'iminsi mikuru no mu byumweru byakurikiyeho kubera icyorezo cy'indwara y'ubwandu bw'agakoko kitari cyarigeze kizwi.
Iyi virusi isa neza na koronavirusi (CoV) yateje indwara y'ubuhumekero ikaze cyane (SARS) mu 2003; Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryayise SARS-CoV-2 ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, kandi indwara itera yitwa CoV Disease-19 (COVID-19).
Iki cyorezo cyatangiriye mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa, kandi cyahise gikwirakwira mu gihugu cyose ndetse no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 ku isi.
Ku ya 2 Werurwe 2020, virusi yari imaze gutuma abantu barenga 80,000 bagaragaweho COVID-19, abarenga 40,000 bakize naho abarenga 3,000 bapfa.
OMS iraburira ko COVID-19 ari "umwanzi wa mbere" kandi ko ishobora guteza akaga gakomeye kurusha iterabwoba.
Nk'uko PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/) ibivuga, mu gihe kitarenze amezi abiri, inyandiko zisaga 200 z'ibanze z'ubushakashatsi ku cyorezo cya COVID-19 zagiye zisohoka, zirimo amakuru y'ubwandu, ubwandu, impamvu, ibipimo n'uburyo bwo kuvurwa kuva raporo ya mbere yo ku ya 7 Mutarama 2020 yagaragaje ko virusi yabonetse mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga mu barwayi batandukanye.
Ubu bushakashatsi bugamije kwigisha ubushakashatsi bwakozwe kuri iki kibuga gishya cy'imikino gikomeje gutera imbere ku mibare myinshi.
Mu ntangiriro, tugiye kugereranya COVID-19 na SARS n'indi ndwara iterwa na CoV, Middle East respiratory syndrome (MERS, yatangiye mu 2012).
Nanone tuzasuzuma ibyo twize ku birebana no kwirinda indwara, hamwe n'ibindi bibazo by'ingenzi bitarashubijwe.
CoVs zari zisanzwe zitezwe nk'indwara idateje akaga ku bantu, zitewe n'ibyago bigera kuri 15% by'ibicurane bisanzwe 4.
Nyamara, muri iki kinyejana, twabonye CoVs ebyiri zangiza abantu, SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, zatumye abantu batangira kwandura mu Bushinwa mu 2003 na Arabiya Sawudite mu 2012, kandi zihita zikwirakwira mu bindi bihugu ziteza indwara n'urupfu.
Ku bw'ibyo, COVID-19 iriho ubu ni CoV ya gatatu yanduye mu mateka y'abantu.
Nkuko bigaragara ku ishusho. ishusho.1,1, abarwayi ba nimoniya batamenyekanye aho bakomoka batangiye kumenyekana i Wuhan ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 kuri Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima y'u Bushinwa.
Nyuma y'iminsi irindwi, urutonde rwa CoV rwasohotse.
Ku ya 15 Mutarama 2020, umurwayi wa mbere wanduye uturutse i Wuhan yaramenyekanye.
Muri icyo gihe, iyo ndwara yakwirakwiriye mu mijyi no mu bihugu byo hafi aho.
Ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama, abaganga batangaje ko iyi ndwara ishobora kwandura abantu binyuze mu kuyandura.
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, umujyi wa Wuhan warafunzwe kandi ingendo zose z'abantu ku isi zarahagaritswe.
Ku ya 24 Mutarama, ubushakashatsi bwa mbere bwakozwe ku byerekeye iki cyorezo bwagaragaje ko mu barwayi 41 bari bamaze kwemezwa, 21 gusa ari bo baguye ku isoko ry'amafi rya Wuhan, aho byitezwe ko icyorezo cyatangiriye ku nyamaswa zitazwi.
Ku ya 30 Mutarama, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari ikibazo cy'ingorabahizi ku buzima ku isi.
Mu gihe iyi raporo yatangazwaga, icyorezo cyari cyamaze gukwirakwira mu Bushinwa no mu bihugu bigera kuri 50 ku isi hose (Ifoto (Ifoto.2).2).
Uko imimerere igenda ihinduka, ni na ko bigenda bigera ku bintu bikomeye.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bantu 8,866 bari bafite COVID-19 4,021 bwemeje ko virusi iherutse kuvumburwa (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
SARS-CoV-2 yibasira abantu b'imyaka yose ariko cyane cyane abafite hagati ya 30 na 65.
Hafi kimwe cya kabiri (47.7%) cy'abarwayi bari bafite imyaka irenga 50, bake bari munsi ya 20, kandi abarwayi 14 gusa bari munsi y'imyaka 10.
SARS-CoV-2 yagaragaye mu bagabo benshi (0.31/100,000) kurusha abagore (0.27/100,000).
COVID-19 ikomeje kwiyongera mu baturage kurusha mu ntara ya Hubei n'uturere tuyikikije.
COVID-19 yamaze iminsi igera kuri 5 (2-9) kuva itangira kugeza igihe yamenyekaniye.
Ibi bimenyetso by'iyi ndwara byamaze iminsi igera kuri 4,8.
Kuva igihe yabonekeye kugeza apfuye, byatwaye iminsi 9,5 (4.8-13).
Umubare w'abarwayi ku gipimo cy'ibanze cy'ubwiyongere (R0) wari 3.77 (95% CI: 3.51-4.05), naho igipimo cya R0 cyasimbuwe cyari 2.23-4.82.
Umubare w'abanduye wiyongereye mbere ya 23 Mutarama 2020, kubera ingendo nyinshi z'abantu mbere y'umunsi mukuru w'impeshyi mu Bushinwa.
Imfu z'abarwayi zari 1.44% (95% CI: 1.10-1.86%), mu gihe umubare w'abarwayi bapfuye wari 3.06% (95% CI: 2.02-4.59%).
Ibibazo bitatu by'indwara ya COVID-19 byari: imibonano mpuzabitsina (abagabo), imyaka (≥60), na nimoniya ikomeye.
CoVs ni ubwoko bw'indwara z'ibyorezo zikomeye kandi z'ibicurane bifite RNA imwe.
