Cytokine storm ni igisubizo cy'umubiri gifite akamaro bitewe no gusohora cytokines zitandukanye zirimo TNFα, IL-1β, IL-2, IL-6, IFNα, IFNβ, IFNγ, na MCP-1.
Izi cytochines zituma abasirikare b'umubiri batanga molekile nyinshi cyane cyane zituma indwara ya ARDS n'ibindi bice by'umubiri bitagenda neza.
Kugabanya ibisebe ni ingenzi mu kuvura ibiza bya sitokine, cyane cyane ku barwayi barembye.
Korticosteroids na tocilizumab, ni umuti wa monoclonal anti-IL6, wakoreshejwe mu kuvura ibicurane by'imyakura.
Ubundi buryo bwo kuvura cytochine bw'inkubi y'umuyaga bwo kugabanya ubukana burimo guhuza ibisubizo by'umubiri bigenzurwa na T-cell; guhagarika IFN-γ, IL-1, na TNF; kubuza JAK; blinatumomab; guhagarika ibimenyetso bya cytochine 4; na HDAC inhibitors.
