Nubwo ari iby'ingenzi ko dushaka ibisubizo by'ibyo bibazo n'ibindi, bishobora kudusaba igihe.
Ahubwo, uko ibyo byaba biri kose, nta kundi twabigenza uretse guhita dukira indwara kandi tukongera kubaho nk'uko bisanzwe.
Virusi ya corona ituruka ku nyamaswa
Ihinduka ry'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima ryatumye virusi ya corona (CoVs) n'inyamaswa zibamo, harimo n'abantu, bihinduka mu gihe cy'imyaka ibarirwa mu bihumbi.
Mbere ya 2003, hari ubwoko bubiri bwa virusi itera indwara zo mu bantu (HCoVs) byari bizwiho gutera indwara zidakomeye, nk'ibicurane bisanzwe.
Icyorezo cya SARS na MERS byatangiye kugaragaza ko HCoV ishobora guhitana abantu benshi.
Icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 mu Bushinwa rwagati mu mpera za 2019 cyongeye kugarura CoVs mu cyumba cy'indembe kandi cyadutangaje cyane n'uburyo cyandura vuba kandi mu buryo budahangayikishije ugereranyije na SARS-CoV.
HCoVs zikomoka ku nyamaswa kandi kumenya inkomoko y'inyamaswa za HCoVs ni ingenzi.
HCoVs nyinshi zituruka mu bihaha kandi ntizirwara.
Hari inyamaswa zimwe na zimwe HCoVs zisanzwe zisanzwe zisanzwe zifite ubushobozi bwo kwanduza mbere yo kugera ku bantu.
Kumenya iby'inyamaswa zitera abantu indwara ni ingenzi mu kurwanya indwara z'abantu.
Gusuzuma imiterere y'inyamaswa zifite CoV na byo bishobora gufasha kumenya ingaruka za CoV ku bantu.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, twavuze muri make ibyagezweho ku ndwara zirindwi za HCoVs, dushyira imbere amateka yazo, aho zakomotse n'uburyo zikwirakwira mu nyamaswa.
Icy'ingenzi ni uko tugaragaza aho HCoVs zitandukanye zihuriye n'aho zinyuranye hakurikijwe uko virusi ihinduka n'uko ibinyabuzima byongera guhurira.
Icyorezo cya CoV disease 2019 (COVID-19) ni cyo cyibanzeho muri iyi nkuru.
Ikindi kandi, uburyo ibinyabuzima byanduye bihinduka n'uko virusi ihinduka ni byo bigaragaza ko indwara ikomeye.
Virusi za corona (CoVs) ziri mu muryango wa Coronaviridae, ugizwe n'itsinda ry'indwara z'ibicurane, buri imwe ifite ibimenyetso by'indwara, kandi ifite RNA imwe.
Iyi virusi ifite genome nini cyane kuri 26 kuri 32 kilobases muri RNA, yitwa CoVs kubera imiterere yayo isa n'ikamba iyo ibonetse mu cyuma cy'umusemburo.
Mu byibanze, CoVs zifite genome zitagizweho ibice kandi ziteraniye hamwe.
Hafi bibiri bya gatatu bya jenome bigizwe n'udupira tubiri tw'ingenzi cyane (ORF1a na ORF1b), dutanga za poroteyine ebyiri za pp1a na pp1ab.
Ibyo bice by'umubiri na byo bihinduka za poroteyine 16 zitagira imiterere, zitwa nsp1~16.
Igice gisigaye cya jenome kiba gifite ORFs ku poroteyine z'imiterere, harimo spike (S), envelope (E), membrane (M) na nucleoprotein (N).
Poroteyine nyinshi z'inyongera zihariye ku bwoko (lineage-specific accessory proteins) nazo zashyizwe mu bwoko butandukanye bwa CoVs.
Bitewe n'ubwoko butandukanye bwa poroteyine, CoVs zashyizwe mu byiciro bine by'ingenzi (alpha-CoV, beta-CoV, gamma-CoV na delta-CoV), aho beta-CoV ari yo ifite umubare munini wa HCoVs kandi igabanyijemo imiryango ine (A, B, C na D).
Ibisubizo by'ubushakashatsi byerekana ko udukoko n'imbeba ari byo bitanga alpha-CoVs na beta-CoVs cyane, mu gihe inyoni ari zo zitanga gamma-CoVs na delta-CoVs cyane.
Mu myaka ibarirwa mu bihumbi, CoVs yagiye ivuka mu nyamaswa kandi zimwe muri zo zagiye zitera indwara mu bantu.
Kugeza ubu, hamaze kumenyekana CoVs zirindwi z'abantu (HCoVs).
Muri izo HCoVs, HCoV-229E na HCoV-NL63 ni izo mu bwoko bwa alpha-CoVs.
Izindi beta-CoV eshanu ni HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, coronavirus y'indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero (SARS-CoV), coronavirus y'indwara y'ubuhumekero yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS-CoV) na SARS-CoV-2.
HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 na HCoV-NL63 akenshi zitera indwara nke, nk'ibicurane bisanzwe na/cyangwa ibicurane.
Mu buryo bunyuranye n'ubwo, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 nshya zashyizwe ahagaragara zirwaye cyane, zigira ingaruka ku gice cyo hasi cy'ubwonko mu barwayi benshi kandi ziteza ibyago byinshi byo kurwara indwara z'ubuhumekero (acute respiratory distress syndrome, ARDS) n'ibimenyetso byo hanze y'ibihaha (extrapulmonary manifestations).
Ubwoko bwa mbere bwa HCoV-229E, B814, bwavumbuwe mu mitsi y'abarwayi ba virusi ya grippe mu myaka ya za 1960.
Kuva icyo gihe, hari ibindi bintu byavumbuwe binyuze mu bushakashatsi bwimbitse kuri HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43, byombi bikaba byaratumye habaho ibimenyetso byigaragaza.
Mu by'ukuri, kugeza igihe SARS yadutse, abantu benshi bemeraga ko kwandura HCoVs muri rusange nta cyo bitwaye.
Icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2003 ni kimwe mu byorezo by'indwara z'ibyorezo by'indwara z'ibyorezo mu mateka ya vuba aha, cyibasiye abantu barenga 8.000, abantu 10% bari bitezwe gupfa.
Nyuma y'imyaka icumi, indwara y'ubuhumekero yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (Middle East respiratory syndrome, MERS) yatumye haba icyorezo mu karere k'inyanja ya Arabiya Sawudite, nyuma kiza gukwirakwira no mu bindi bice by'isi.
2019 novel HCoV (2019-nCoV), yaje kwitwa SARS-CoV-2, ni yo mpamvu y'icyorezo cya coronavirus cy'ubwandu bwa 2019 (COVID-19), cyahitanye abantu barenga 3,120 kandi cyandura abantu barenga 91,000 guhera ku ya 3 Werurwe 2020.
Inanga zarasonnye kandi isi igomba kwitegura icyorezo cy'isi yose cya SARS-CoV-2.
HCoVs zose uko ari ndwi zituruka ku mikorobe, imbeba cyangwa amatungo arerwa mu ngo.
Hari ibimenyetso byinshi bigaragaza ko HCoVs zose zikomoka mu mbeba, aho virusi ziba zisanzwe kandi zidakora, ariko zigira imiterere itandukanye cyane.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyateje ibibazo bikomeye mu buvuzi, siyansi, imibereho myiza y'abantu n'imyitwarire mu Bushinwa no ku isi.
Gukurikirana inkomoko ya HCoVs mu nyamaswa bituma tumenya amateka, ibyatumye iyo virusi idashobora kwanduzwa n'inyamaswa.
Ibi kandi bishobora gutuma hashyirwaho ingamba zihuse zo gushaka inyamaswa zitwara SARS-CoV-2 kuva ku nyamaswa z'ibanze kugeza ku bantu, bikaba bifite ibisobanuro bikomeye mu kwirinda icyorezo kizaza.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, hatanzwe amakuru ku nkomoko ya HCoV mu matungo, uburyo ikwirakwira mu matungo atandukanye n'ingaruka z'ubwandu.
By'umwihariko, twatanze ibitekerezo kandi turaganira ku gitekerezo rusange cy'uko HCoVs z'inkomoko zidakora ku buzima bw'inyamaswa ariko zigakora ku buzima bw'inyamaswa iyo zigiye mu zindi.
Nanone kandi, twasuzumye uko virusi ya HCoV ihinduka uko ikomeza kwanduzwa kandi kenshi ikagira ingaruka nke ku buzima.
Ingaruka z'icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 kiriho ubu na zo zirimo kuvugwa muri iki cyiciro.
CoVs ziterwa n'inyamaswa zamenyekanye kuva mu mpera z'imyaka ya za 30.
Mbere y'uko virusi ya HCoV-229E yo mu bwoko bwa B814 itandukanywa n'imyanda y'abarwayi ba virusi ya grippe, CoV nyinshi zari zaratandukanyijwe n'inyamaswa nyinshi zanduye, harimo ingurube, imbeba, inka, ingurube, injangwe n'imbwa.
Mu binyejana bishize, hamaze kuvumburwa HCoVs zirindwi.
Amateka magufi y'ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bwoko bwa HCoV (Ikubo 1) azagira icyo atwigisha.
HCoV-229E yabonetse bwa mbere mu bantu barwaye indwara z'ubuhumekero mu mwaka wa 1966, kandi yagaragaye mu bwoko bw'ingirabuzimafatizo zo mu bihaha za WI-38.
Abarwayi banduye HCoV-229E bagaragaje ibimenyetso bya virusi ya grippe, harimo umutwe, kwitsamura, kuribwa mu muhogo, umuriro n'inkorora mu barwayi 10~20%.
Nyuma mu 1967, HCoV-OC43 yavumbuwe mu buhinzi bw'ingingo hanyuma mu buhinzi bw'imbeba mu bwonko bw'imbeba.
Ibimenyetso by'uburwayi biterwa na HCoV-OC43 bisa n'ibya HCoV-229E, ariko ibimenyetso byayo ntibitandukanye n'iby'izindi virusi z'ibicurane nka influenza A na rhinoviruses.
HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43 byombi bigenda ku isi hose, kandi akenshi bigenda mu gihe cy'itumba mu bihe by'ubukonje.
Ubusanzwe, ibimenyetso by'iyo mikorobe byamara igihe kitageze ku cyumweru, nyuma yaho hakagira igihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri umuntu arwaye.
Dukurikije ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bitangiye gukora, abantu bari bazima banduye HCoV-229E basanganywe ibicurane bisanzwe.
Abarwayi bake bari bafite ibihaha bito ni bo bakomeretse cyane mu gice cyo hasi cy'ibihaha.
SARS, izwi kandi nka atypical pneumonia, ni icyorezo cya mbere cyandujwe na HCoV mu mateka y'isi kandi cyatewe na SARS-CoV, ubwoko bwa gatatu bwa HCoV bwamenyekanye.
Umurwayi wa mbere wa SARS yavumbuwe mu mpera za 2002 mu Ntara ya Guangdong mu Bushinwa.
Icyorezo cya SARS cyateje abantu 8.096 bamenyekanye kandi gihitana abantu 774, mu bihugu byinshi no ku migabane myinshi.
Uretse ubwandu bw'indwara zisanzwe, byemejwe ko buri murwayi ashobora kwandura abandi bantu babiri, ibimenyetso bikigaragara mu minsi 4 kugeza ku minsi 7 nyuma y'umunsi wa 10 w'ubwandu.
Abarwayi banduye SARS-CoV batangira bafite ububabare mu ngingo, umutwe, umuriro, gusinzira no kuruka, bikurikirwa no guhumeka nabi, gukorora no guhumeka nabi.
Imyorezo y'amaraso, ibizamini byo kugabanyuka kw'imikorere y'umwijima, hamwe n'umubare munini wa creatine kinase ni bimwe mu bibazo bya SARS bigaragara mu bipimo byo gupima.
Ingaruka z'ibihaha (gusenyuka kwa alveolar), kugabanuka kw'ingirabuzimafatizo z'uruhu (epithelial cell proliferation) no kwiyongera kw'imyanya ndangagitsina ituruka ku mikorobe na byo byaravuzwe mu barwayi ba SARS.
Hafi ya 20-30% by'abarwayi bakeneye ubuvuzi bwihuse n'ibikoresho by'ubuhumekero.
Uretse igice cyo hasi cy'igifu, ibice byinshi birimo urwungano rw'igifu, ibibembe n'impyiko na byo bishobora kwangirika muri ibi bihe bikomeye, akenshi bijyana n'inkubi y'umuyaga wa cytokine, bishobora guhitana cyane cyane abarwayi bafite igifu gito.
Iyi virusi yagaragaye bwa mbere mu nyama yakuwe mu bihaha bya mwene wabo w'umurwayi wa mbere wageze muri Hong Kong avuye i Guangzhou.
Kuva icyo gihe, hakozwe ubushakashatsi bwinshi kuri HCoV.
HCoV-NL63 yagaragaye mu mwana w'amezi 7 wo mu Buholandi mu mpera za 2004.
Mu mizo ya mbere, byagaragaraga ko ari byinshi mu bana bato, abasaza n'abarwayi bafite ibihaha bito kandi bafite indwara ziterwa n'ibisebe.
Kurwara indwara y'ibicurane, ibicurane, malariya, no kwandura ibicurane by'ibihaha (bronchiolitis) ni ibintu bikunze kugaragara mu ndwara ziterwa na HCoV-NL63.
Ubundi bushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko virusi imwe yabonetse mu isuzuma ry'amazuru y'umwana w'umuhungu w'amezi 8 wari urwaye ibicurane mu Buholandi.
Nubwo icyo cyorezo cyavumbuwe mu Buholandi, mu by'ukuri cyakwirakwiriye ku isi hose.
Bivugwa ko HCoV-NL63 ari yo nyirabayazana wa 4,7% by'indwara z'ubuhumekero, kandi ikunda kwibasira abantu mu itangira ry'impeshyi, itumba n'itumba.
HCoV-NL63 ifitanye isano n'indwara y'ubuhumekero (obstructive laryngitis, cyangwa croup).
Muri uwo mwaka, HCoV-HKU1 yagaragaye mu mugabo w'imyaka 71 wari urwaye igituntu n'imyanda yo mu bihaha i Hong Kong.
Uretse ibicurane n'imyanda yo mu bihaha, HCoV-HKU1 kandi yagaragaye ifitanye isano no kwiyongera kw'indwara y'ibicurane.
Kimwe na HCoV-NL63, HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 yagaragaye ku isi hose, ituma indwara z'ubuhumekero zidakomera.
Izi HCoV zose uko ari enye zirazwi kandi muri rusange ntiziteganyijwe guhinduka ngo zitere indwara zikomeye, nubwo habayeho impanuka ziterwa n'impamvu zitazwi nk'ubwoko butandukanye bwa HCoV-NL63, buherutse kugaragara ko bwateje indwara zikomeye mu karere k'uburasirazuba bw'u Bushinwa.
Muri rusange, HCoVs zigira ubushobozi bwo kugenda neza no kuba mu bantu, kandi zigenda zihinduka zidakomeye cyane.
MERS-CoV yagaragaye bwa mbere mu 2012 mu bihaha by'umurwayi w'imyaka 60 wari urwaye ibicurane bikomeye n'impyiko zidakora neza muri Arabie Saoudite.
Nubwo abarwayi bose banduye bakomoka mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati, abarwayi baturutse hanze bagaragaye mu bihugu byinshi by'i Burayi na Tuniziya.
Mu mwaka wa 2015, muri Koreya y'Epfo higeze kwaduka icyorezo cy'iyi ndwara, abantu 186 bakaba barayanduye.
Ibimenyetso bya MERS birasa cyane na SARS, aho indwara y'ibihaha ikomeje kwiyongera.
Mu buryo butandukanye na SARS, abarwayi benshi ba MERS na bo bagize ikibazo cy'impyiko, ubu MERS ni yo yonyine mu ndwara ziterwa na HCoV.
Abarenga 30% by'abarwayi bagira ibibazo byo mu mara, nko kugira iseseme no guhema.
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare 2020, abarwayi barenga 2500 bemejwe mu igerageza bari bafite igipimo cyo gupfa cya 34.4%, bigatuma MERS-CoV iba imwe muri virusi zangiza cyane abantu.
Hagati no mu mpera z'Ukuboza 2019, abarwayi ba nimoniya bazwiho SARS-CoV-2 bagaragaye i Wuhan, mu Ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangaje ko icyorezo cy'indwara y'ibihaha iterwa na SARS-CoV-2 ari ikibazo cy'ingorabahizi mu buzima bw'abaturage gihangayikishije amahanga yose, kandi ko icyorezo ari COVID-19.
Kugeza ku ya 3 Werurwe 2020, abantu 90,053 ni bo bari baranduye ku isi hose, aho umubare w'abapfa wari 3.4%.
Ni ngombwa kumenya ko mu Bushinwa, umubare w'abandura bapfa muri Hubei uri kuri 4,2%, mu gihe hanze yawo ari 1,2%.
SARS-CoV-2 iteza indwara ikomeye mu mubiri nk'uko bimeze kuri SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, ikaba ifite ibimenyetso nk'umuriro, gukorora no guhumeka nabi.
Hari n'abarwayi bamwe na bamwe bafite ikibazo cy'umushongi.
Indwara ya Pneumonia ni kimwe mu bimenyetso bikomeye kandi bishobora kwiyongera vuba bigatuma umuntu agira ibibazo byo guhumeka.
Nubwo SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 zifite aho zihuriye cyane mu buryo bwa homologie y'urusobe rwa nucleotide iri hejuru ya 82%, zigaragara ku mashami atandukanye y'igiti cy'inkomoko.
SARS-CoV-2 ni indwara yoroheje ariko ikwirakwira cyane ugereranyije na SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV.
Abarwayi ba SARS-CoV-2 batagaragaza ibimenyetso baramaze kugaragara kandi bashobora gufasha mu kwihutisha ikwirakwira ryayo ku isi.
Kugereranya no guhura kwa SARS-CoV-2 n'izindi HCoV esheshatu byagaragaje ibintu bitandukanye bisabwa.
Icya mbere, igihe ibimenyetso by'indwara zitangira kugaragara n'igihe virusi ya HCoV imara mu mubiri bisa cyane.
Muri ubwo buryo, SARS-CoV-2 ikurikiza imiterere y'izindi HCoV esheshatu.
Icya kabiri, ubukana bw'ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 buhuriye ku bwoko bwa SARS-CoV n'ubwoko bune bwa HCoVs (ni ukuvuga HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 na HCoV-NL63).
Ku ruhande rumwe, umuntu urwaye SARS-CoV-2 aba afite ibimenyetso bisanzwe bigaragara ku bantu barwaye HCoVs, harimo ibimenyetso bidasanzwe, byoroheje cyangwa nta bimenyetso na mba.
Ku rundi ruhande, abantu bake banduye COVID-19 bashobora kugaragara nk'abanduye SARS-CoV, nubwo umubare wabo waba muto.
Icya gatatu, ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV-2 na ryo rigaragaza imiterere y'ibisanzwe y'ikwirakwira rya HCoVs na SARS-CoV.
Ku ruhande rumwe, SARS-CoV-2 ikwirakwira cyane nk'uko bimeze kuri HCoVs.
Ku rundi ruhande, ntibiramenyekana niba SARS-CoV-2 igabanya ubukana nyuma yo kwanduzwa n'abantu nk'uko bimeze kuri SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV.
Icya nyuma, kimwe n'izindi HCoVs, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kugaragara mu bipimo by'ubwandu.
Kuba SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kwandura umuntu mu buryo buteye ubwoba nk'uko bimeze kuri SARS-CoV mu bihe bimwe na bimwe bigomba kwemezwa n'ubushakashatsi buzakorwa mu gihe kiri imbere.
Ni ngombwa kandi kureba niba SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kuba yaragize igihe cyo kwizigamira nk'uko bimeze kuri HCoVs.
Nubwo bimeze bityo ariko, amakuru ya SARS-CoV-2 arimo ubwandu, ubwandu bw'indwara n'ubwandu bw'abantu buzakomeza kugira uruhare mu gutuma COVID-19 ikwirakwira.
Ibimenyetso byose byoroheje biterwa na HCoVs abantu barabihanganira neza.
Mu yandi magambo, birashoboka ko abantu bashobora kuba bafite ubushobozi bwo kwirinda HCoVs.
Mu yandi magambo, byombi bishobora kuba ari byo byonyine byakize virusi ya HCoV yari imaze igihe kirekire.
HCoVs zateye indwara z'ubwoko bwinshi mu bantu n'abantu banduye HCoV z'ubwoko bwinshi zarakemutse.
Kugira ngo ibyo bibe, HCoVs zigomba kwiyongera mu bantu inshuro zihagije kugira ngo umubare wazo ushobore guhangana n'ingaruka z'imiterere y'umuntu cyangwa ikintu.
Ku bw'ibyo, uko SARS-CoV-2 igenda irushaho kugabanuka kandi ikandura abantu benshi, ni na ko amahirwe yayo yo kwihanganira abantu agenda yiyongera.
Iyo iki cyorezo cyamaze kumenyekana neza, gukwirakwira kwacyo hagati y'abantu biragoye kugihagarika binyuze mu gufunga abantu cyangwa mu bindi bikorwa byo kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'indwara.
Mu myaka myinshi, ubwoko bune bwa CoVs bwakwirakwijwe mu bantu butera ibicurane bisanzwe mu bantu bafite uburwayi.
Iyo mikorobe ntiyihishe mu matungo.
Mu buryo butandukanye, virusi z'indwara z'ibyorezo SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV ntiziramenyekana neza kandi ntizishobora gukwirakwira mu bantu.
Igomba kuba ihora mu karere ikoreramo kandi ikagenzura uburyo bwo gushyigikira abantu bafite intege nke, wenda binyuriye ku muntu umwe cyangwa benshi bafite intege nke mu buryo bw'umubiri.
Virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 ifite ibimenyetso bisa cyane na SARS-CoV/MERS-CoV hamwe na virusi enye zandura abantu mu buryo bw'ibanze zitwa HCoVs.
Iyo virusi ikwirakwira cyane nk'iyo mu bantu, nibura nk'uko ubu bizwi.
Icyakora, ni yo ituma abantu barwara cyane kurusha HCoVs kandi ntiziteza indwara nyinshi nk'iyo SARS-CoV cyangwa MERS-CoV.
Kugeza ubu biracyari mu iperereza niba iyi virusi ishobora kwihanganira abantu kandi ikwirakwira mu bantu nta cyo ibaye cyangwa ikwirakwira mu nyamaswa zitagira ubwandu.
Mbere yo kuvuga ku nyamaswa zanduza HCoVs, birakwiriye ko tubanza gusobanura neza icyo ayo magambo asobanura n'ibimenyetso byayo, imiterere, imiterere, ikwirakwira, aho virusi idashobora kwanduza n'aho virusi ishobora kwanduza HCoVs.
Inyamaswa ikora nk'ikinyamubiri cyanduza HCoV iyo ifite imiterere y'ibinyabuzima nk'ibya mbere mu gusangira ibinyabuzima ku rwego rwa selile.
Akenshi, virusi z'ubwoko runaka ziba zitamenyereye aho ziba kandi ntizitera indwara aho ziba.
Mu buryo nk'ubwo, virusi itera HCoV ikomeza kubaho igihe kirekire.
Muri ibyo bihe byombi, ubwandu bw'agakoko gatera SIDA ni ubwandu kandi ni ubwandu bwa HCoV cyangwa se ubwandu bw'agakoko.
Mu buryo bunyuranye n'ubwo, iyo virusi ya HCoV igeze mu bantu mbere cyangwa mu gihe cy'ubwandu, iba itaramenyereye aho ituye kandi ishobora kwanduza.
Aho virusi idashobora kwandura iba ishobora kuba isoko y'indwara mu bantu kandi ikagira uruhare mu gutuma virusi yandura ikongera ikandura abantu kandi igatuma indwara ikwirakwira mu bantu.
HCoV ntizishobora gukwirakwira mu gihe zidashobora kwibeshaho ku kintu kitanduye.
Mu yandi magambo, HCoVs zishobora kwihanganira imiterere y'ubwandu bw'indwara kandi zigakomeza kuba indwara mu gihe kirekire.
Ibyo bituma ubumara butagira icyo bukora buhinduka ubumara bw'ibinyabuzima.
Amakuru y'indwara yagaragaje ko SARS yaturutse ku nyamaswa zo mu gasozi.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku iriba bwagaragaje ko abacuruzi b'amatungo bafite abasirikare barwanya SARS-CoV IgG benshi mu mubiri ugereranyije n'abandi bantu.
Ibirura (Paguma larvata) n'imbwa zo muri Aziya zitwa racoon byabonetse ko zanduye SARS-CoV, zisa cyane na SARS-CoV.
Ibi byatewe inkunga n'uko nyuma yo kwica izo nyamaswa zari mu isoko, virusi ya SARS ntizongeye kugaragara.
Ariko, inyamaswa zo mu gasozi cyangwa mu gasozi mbere yo kujya ku isoko ntizagira virusi ya SARS-CoV, bivuze ko iyo nyamaswa ishobora kuba ifite virusi ariko ntiyikwirakwize ariko atari ikinyabuzima cya SARS-CoV.
Kubera ko 80% by'amatungo atandukanye yo mu isoko rya Guangzhou afite abarwayi barwanya SARS-CoV, ntidushobora kwirengagiza ko utwo dukoko duto duto dushobora kuba dufite ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV.
Ibi byose bisa n'aho byatewe na virusi ya SARS-CoV ariko ntibikwirakwizwe.
Ingaruka zabaye iz'uko inyamaswa y'inyamaswa ifite virusi ya SARS-CoV yagaragaje ko ifite imiterere nk'iy'iyo muri CoV ya SARS Rhinolophus bat CoV HKU3 (SARSr-Rh-BatCoV HKU3), iboneka mu ndwara y'ingwe yo mu Bushinwa.
Iyi virusi ifite abasirikare barwanya SARS-CoV na BatCoV HKU3.
Iyi ni indi virusi ya CoV ifite ubushobozi bwo guhitana virusi nyinshi, ifite 88-92% by'ubwoko bwa SARS-CoV.
Ubwo bushakashatsi bwashyizeho urufatiro rw'ubumenyi bushya bw'uko utugingo duto duto duto tw'inyamaswa twanduza indwara nshya z'abantu.
Hari izindi virusi nyinshi zisa na SARS CoVs (SL-CoVs) na zo zavumbuwe mu mbeba ariko nta zindi uretse WIV1 zishobora gutandukanywa nk'indwara nzima.
Ingirabuzima fatizo yitwa angiotensin converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) ni yo izwiho kuba ari yo ituma SARS-CoV ifata abantu.
WIV1 yakuwe mu bipimo by'ibicurane by'imbeba kandi yagaragaye ikoresha imbeba, inguge na ACE2 mu bantu mu kurwanya ubwandu bw'indwara.
Igishimishije ni uko virusi ya SARS mu barwayi bakize yashoboraga guhashya WIV1.
Nubwo bimeze bityo ariko, WIV1 igereranya umuryango wa hafi wa SARS-CoV mu mbeba, usangiye 95% by'ibinyabuzima.
Uretse kuba izo virusi zombi zifite ibintu byinshi zihuriyeho, biremerwa ko WIV1 atari virusi ya SARS-CoV, kandi ko SARS-CoV na yo atari virusi ya SARS.
Ubushakashatsi ku mpinduka z'imiterere y'ingirabuzima fatizo bwashyize MERS-CoV mu itsinda rimwe na CoV-HKU4 na CoV-HKU5.
Inzoka za CoV-HKU4 na MERS-CoV zikoresha ikinyabutabire kimwe, dipeptidyl peptidase 4 (DPP4), mu kwinjiza virusi.
ADN (RNA) ya MERS-CoV ihuriyeho n'iyo mu mbeba beta-CoVs zabonetse mu Burayi no muri Afurika.
Nubwo bimeze bityo ariko, nta virusi ya MERS-CoV nzima ishobora kuboneka mu ducurama.
MERS-CoV na CoV-HKU25 ifite ibice 87% by'ibinyabuzima bihuriyeho.
Icyo gihe, ibibyimba bishobora kuba atari byo byanduza virusi ya MERS-CoV.
Ku rundi ruhande, ubushakashatsi bwakorewe mu bihugu by'iburasirazuba bwo hagati bwagaragaje ko ingamiya z'iburasirazuba bwo hagati zanduye MERS-CoV, nk'uko byagenze ku ngamiya zo muri Afurika zaturutse mu burasirazuba bwo hagati.
Virusi ya MERS-CoV ni virusi isa n'iyo mu bantu yabonetse mu mwonko w'ingamiya, ibyo bikaba byerekana ko ingamiya zisanzwe zanduye virusi ya MERS-CoV.
Ni ngombwa ko ibimenyetso byoroheje ariko by'indwara y'ibicurane byigaragaza mu ngamiya zanduye MERS-CoV.
Uzirikane ko ingamiya zanduye zidakomoka ku mwuka gusa, ahubwo ko ingamiya ari yo mpamvu ikomeye cyane y'indwara zanduye.
Ariko, ibibazo biracyariho kuko abarwayi ba MERS basanzwemo nta muntu n'umwe bahuye na we mbere y'uko ibimenyetso biboneka, bishobora kuba biterwa n'ubwandu bw'umuntu ku wundi cyangwa se ubwandu butamenyekanye bw'ubwoko butamenyekanye bw'inyamaswa zanduye MERS-CoV.
SARS-CoV-2 ifite 96.2% by'ibinyabuzima bimwe na CoV RaTG13 yavuye mu mbeba yitwa Rhinolophus affinis.
Kandi kimwe na SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, itandukaniro hagati ya SARS-CoV-2 na RaTG13 ni rinini cyane ku buryo bigoye kumenya isano iri hagati y'iyo virusi.
Ni ukuvuga ko udukoko dushobora kuba tutari tworoshye kwandura SARS-CoV-2 keretse tubonye udukoko dutandukanye.
Mu buryo bw'ibanze, inyamaswa ifite virusi idashobora kwanduza SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kuba ari imwe mu nyamaswa zigurishwa mu ishyamba kandi zikicwa ku isoko rya Huanan Seafood Wholesale Market, aho icyorezo cya mbere cya COVID-19 cyabanje gufatwa nk'aho ari ikwirakwira ry'indwara y'inyamaswa-ku-bantu.
Ubushakashatsi butandukanye bwa mbere bushingiye ku ivugurura ry'imiterere y'ingirabuzima fatizo bwemeje ko ubwoko bw'inyamaswa zo mu bwoko bwa pangolins (Manis javanica) ziri mu kaga zishobora kuba zifite ibinyabuzima birwanya beta-CoVs bisa na SARS-CoV-2.
Iyi ni ubwoko bw'inyamaswa zitari zigeze ziboneka zigize ubwoko bwa CoV-Pangolin, zifite 85-92% by'ibinyabuzima bihuriyeho na SARS-CoV-2.
Ahubwo, ifite aho ihuriye na RaTG13 ku kigero cya 90% ku byerekeye imiterere y'ibinyabuzima.
Batoranyije imirongo ibiri mito ya virusi isa na SARS-CoV-2 mu bwoko bushya bwa virusi, imwe muri yo ikaba ifitanye isano ya genome na (RBD) SARS-CoV-2, aho 97.4% y'ibinyabuzima by'iyo virusi ari bimwe.
Mu igereranya ry'uburyo butandukanye, imikorere ya RBDs ya SARS-CoV-2 na RaTG13 yari itandukanye cyane ariko yari igaragazwa n'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima.
Ubushakashatsi bwa mbere ku nguge zanduye bwagaragaje ko hari virusi mu bihaha byazo ifitanye isano na SARS-CoV-2.
Ubushakashatsi bwakoresheje uburyo butandukanye harimo no guhindura imiterere y'ingirabuzima fatizo zigena uko virusi izamera ku kigero cya 86.3%.
Ntabwo twakwirengagiza ko pangolin ari imwe mu nyamaswa zitwara virusi zitandura SARS-CoV-2.
Kugeza ubu, nta makuru yemewe y'uko SARS-CoV-2 ya pangolin ishobora gutandukana n'indi SARS-CoV-2 na SARS-CoV-2 beta-CoVs ya pangolin.
Mu buryo nk'ubwo, intera iri hagati ya SARS-CoV-2 na RaTG13 ni nto cyane ugereranyije n'iyo hagati ya SARS-CoV-2 na SARS-CoV-2-related beta-CoVs ya pangolin.
Impinduka y'indwara ya SARS-CoV-2 mu birura, mu bifi byo mu bwoko bwa pangolin n'ibindi bikoko bisa n'abantu ntiziramenyekana.
Nubwo hari ihinduka mu maraso ryabonetse hagati ya RBDs na SARS-CoV-2 na pangolin, virusi zifite ibyago byo kwandura SARS-CoV-2 beta-CoVs, SARS-CoV-2 na RaTG13 zisangiye kode.
Biteganyijwe ko guhuza cyane hagati ya RBDs muri virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 beta-CoVs na SARS-CoV-2 bigengwa n'ihinduka ry'imiterere.
Ikindi gitekerezo cy'inyongera gishyigikira isano hagati ya virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 beta-CoV na RaTG13 mu nyamaswa.
Kubera ko ari imbaraga zituma habaho ihinduka ry'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima, nta kwihuza kuranga beta-CoVs.
Icyemezo ntikiremezwa ku nyamaswa zanduye SARS-CoV-2.
Uretse HCoVs z'ingenzi ziterwa n'indwara, hakozwe ubushakashatsi ku nkomoko ya HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-NL63 na HCoV-HKU1 mu nyamaswa.
Amakuru y'ibanze y'ibanze avuga ko HCoV-NL63 na HCoV-229E zishobora kuba zaturutse kuri CoV mu mbeba, mu gihe umuvandimwe wa HCoV-OC43 na HCoV-HKU1 yasanganywe mu rukoko.
Byemejwe ko CoV ya ARCoV.2 (Appalachian Ridge CoV) yaturutse muri Amerika ya Ruguru ifite ibara ry'umweru ry'umweru kandi ko ifitanye isano ya hafi na HCoV-NL63.
Mu yandi magambo, HCoV-229E yagaragaye ko ifite ibinyabuzima bya CoV, Hipposideros/GhanaKwam/19/2008, byatangajwe muri Ghana, kandi ingamiya nazo zitekereza ko ari zo zanduye.
Mu rwego rwo kurushaho gusobanukirwa, ibitekerezo ku nkomoko y'inyamaswa kuri HCoVs zizwi byashyizwe mu ishusho ya 1 n'iya 2.
Ubushakashatsi ku miterere y'ibinyabuzima butanga ibimenyetso byerekana ko HCoVs ikwirakwira mu bwoko bw'inyamaswa bufite ubukana nk'uko byahoze.
Igihe HCoV-OC43 yavaga mu bwoko bumwe ikajya mu bantu binyuze mu matungo y'ubucuruzi mu 1890, indwara y'igifu y'igifu y'igifu yashinzwe.
Amateka y'ubwandu bw'ubwoko butandukanye bwa HCoV-229E ntabwo arasobanutse neza.
Habonetse alpha-CoVs ifite isano ya hafi na HCoV-229E.
Muri izo harimo alpaca alpha-CoV.
Hari amakuru menshi atandukanye ashyigikira ikwirakwira ry'iyi virusi iturutse ku mikorobe ikajya ku bantu.
Mbere na mbere, abantu ni bo bahana imyanya y'ubutaka, ariko si alpacas.
Ahubwo, abantu bafitanye isano ya bugufi na alpacas.
Icya kabiri, HCoV-229E ifitanye isano na alpha-CoVs y'ikinyugunyugu ifite ubwandu butandukanye kandi budafite ubwandu bw'ibicurane, mu gihe alpaca alpha-CoV yatumye indwara iba mu buryo bw'imikorere y'inyamaswa zanduye.
Icya nyuma, alpaca alpha-CoV ntabwo yagaragaye mu nyamaswa zisubiye mu ishyamba.
Ku bw'ibyo, ntibishoboka ko alpacas zazanwa na HCoV-229E ifitanye isano na alpha-CoV iturutse ku bantu.
Mu by'ukuri, udukoko ni two dukoko dutera indwara z'abantu muri icyo gihugu, harimo virusi ya rabies, Ebola, Nipah na Hendra.
Ku bw'ibyo, ntibitangaje kuba udukoko dushobora kwanduza HCoV-229E mu buryo butaziguye abantu.
Mu yandi magambo, nubwo alpha-CoVs ari yo soko y'ibinyabuzima bya HCoV-229E, alpacas na dromedary camels bishobora kuba bifite ubwandu bw'indwara zitandura cyane ku bantu nk'uko bimeze kuri MERS-CoV.
MERS-CoV ni urugero rwiza rw'ubwandu bw'ubwoko butandukanye, kuva ku nguge ujya ku ngamiya no kuva ku ngamiya ujya ku bantu.
Inkomoko y'ihindagurika rya MERS-CoV mu mbeba yari izwi kuva mu ntangiriro kandi ibyo byemejwe n'ubushakashatsi.
Birumvikana ko udukoko duto duto duto tugize ubwoko bwinshi cyane bw'udukoko tuguruka mu bwoko butandukanye, tukagenda twigaragaza mu bwoko butandukanye kandi tukagenda twigaragaza mu bwoko butandukanye.
Kuba ari abantu bareshya batyo, kuba ari mu matsinda menshi, kuba ari abantu bafatanye cyane kandi bafite ubushobozi bwo gusimbuka cyane, byose bituma abo bantu baba abahanga mu gutwara virusi.
Ku rundi ruhande, MERS-CoV yagiye iboneka mu ngamiya (dromedary camels) mu gihe kirekire.
Iyo ngamiya ni yo ifite ubushobozi bwo guhinduka ikagira ubuzima, ikava mu kiraro cy'udukoko tudafite ubushobozi bwo kwanduzanya, ikajya mu kiremwa gifite ubushobozi bwo kwanduzanya.
MERS-CoV ituma indwara zidakunda kubaho kandi ntizikunda kwiyongera cyane mu nyamaswa.
Kwandura kwa virusi ya MERS-CoV ku bantu ni ibintu by'impanuka kandi abantu bakomeza guhura na virusi ya MERS-CoV ariko ntibikwirakwizwe kuko ikwirakwira ryayo ritagenzurwa.
Ugereranyije n'ingamiya mu kwanduza MERS-CoV, ingunzu, iyo ari inyamaswa, mu kwanduza SARS-CoV-2 ifite uruhare rwihariye.
By'umwihariko, virusi beta-CoVs ya pangolin ni yo ahanini iteza indwara mu nguge.
Bishobora kuba ari virusi idahitana beta-CoVs ifitanye isano na SARS-CoV-2, nk'uko bimeze ku busa bwa SARS-CoV.
Ubushobozi bukomeye bwo gukwirakwiza SARS-CoV-2 mu bwoko butandukanye bw'inyamaswa ku bantu bugomba kwemezwa cyangwa guhakanirwa mu bushakashatsi buzakurikiraho.
Mbere na mbere, impumyi zishobora kuba zanduye virusi irwanya SARS-CoV-2 isa cyane na SARS-CoV-2.
Abantu bashobora kugereranya imiterere y'ibyo binyabuzima n'iy'ibumba.
Icya kabiri, ibinyamushongo bishobora kuba ari byo bikurura virusi yanduza SARS-CoV-2 byinjijwe.
Abantu banduzwa n'iyo nyama iyo bayihaye cyangwa bayirya.
Birashoboka ko inyamaswa zo mu ngo zirimo n'iziribwa mu ngo zishobora kwandura SARS-CoV-2.
Kwiga inyamaswa zo mu ngo n'izo mu gasozi kugira ngo umenye uko abanduye bakira indwara z'umubiri bigenda, ni ngombwa.
Icya gatatu, nk'uko byavuzwe haruguru, ikinyuranyo cy'ibinyabuzima na SARS-CoV-2 bishobora kuba byaravuye mu bwoko bwa gatatu bufitanye isano n'imbeba na pangolin.
Ubushakashatsi ku nkomoko ya SARS-CoV-2 mu nyamaswa buracyakomeje.
Uretse ubwoko bw'inyamaswa zanduye, hari ibintu bitatu by'ingenzi ku ruhande rw'indwara kandi bifite akamaro mu gutuma CoVs zitangira guhangana n'inzitizi zo kwanduzanya.
Icya mbere, ni uko ubukana bwayo bufite ubushobozi bwo kuvanaho ibintu byinshi cyane mu buryo bw'ibanze.
Ugereranyije n'izindi virusi z'umwanda umwe (single-stranded RNA viruses), umubare w'ibinyabutabire by'iyo virusi ugereranywa ko uri hagati ya gigandida na gishya ku gipimo kiri hagati ya ~10-4 mu mwaka kuri buri mwanya wa 2, bitewe n'urwego rwa CoV rwo kwihanganira virusi itaramenyekana.
CoVs zimenya gutandukanya exoribonuclease, kandi iyo zitandukanyijwe zituma zidakora cyane cyangwa zidakora.
Igishishikaje ni uko umuti witwa Remdesivir uzwiho kugabanya ikwirakwira rya CoV binyuze mu kubuza exoribonuclease (RNA) ishingiye kuri RNA polymerase.
Remdesivir ni imwe mu miti ya SARS-CoV-2 irimo kugeragezwa mu byiciro by'ubuvuzi.
Ibi byose hamwe, igipimo cyo guhinduranya CoVs ni inshuro miliyoni nyinshi kuruta icy'ubwandu.
Mu buryo nk'ubwo, umubare w'abandura akenshi uba munini cyane iyo CoV idafite ibimenyetso by'ubwandu.
Ugereranyije na SARS-CoV ifite umuvuduko wo guhinduka cyane, SARS-CoV-2 isa n'aho ifite umuvuduko wo guhinduka muke, ibyo bikaba bigaragaza ko ubu imaze kumenyera abantu.
Ashobora kuba yari asanzwe amenyereye ibintu bitandukanye n'ibyo abantu bakunda.
Uretse SARS-CoV-2, ibi kandi birareba MERS-CoV, isanzwe imenyerewe ku ngamiya.
Mu buryo bw'ibanze, birashoboka ko ihinduka ry'imiterere y'ingirabuzima fatizo rishobora gutuma urukingo rwa SARS-CoV-2 rudakora vuba.
Icya kabiri, ingirabuzimafatizo nini ya RNA muri CoVs ihagarika imiterere y'ibinyabuzima binyuranye, bityo ikongera amahirwe yo kwiyongera kw'ubwoko, ibintu byiza mu iterambere ry'ubwoko bwa CoV.
Ibi bishyigikiwe na poroteyine ifite akamaro kanini mu gice cya 3′ cy'urusobe rw'ibinyabuzima.
Icya gatatu, CoVs zikunze guhinduka mu buryo bw'umwihariko mu gihe cyo kubyara binyuze mu buryo bwa koppa-kyun-se.
Mu cyumba cya virusi, impinduka zikomeye ziboneka mu gihe cyo kwandukura RNA ya CoV.
Imiterere y'ibinyabuzima (RNAs) isa cyane hamwe na RNAs zo mu bwoko bw'ibinyabuzima (subgenomic RNAs) bishobora guhura bigakora indi CoV.
Amakuru y'ihinduka ry'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima byavumbuwe muri HCoV-HKU1 na HCoV-OC43, hamwe na CoV z'inyamaswa nka SL-CoV na HCoV-HKU9.
Imigenderanire n'abantu banduye ni yo ituma indwara zikwirakwira
Uretse izo mpamvu eshatu za virusi zavuzwe haruguru, kuba virusi n'ubwandu by'indwara by'ubwoko butandukanye ari byo bituma indwara zikwirakwira.
Muri iki gitabo, SARS-CoV itavugwaho rumwe ifatwa nk'urugero ruzwi rw'ibimenyetso by'indwara y'indwara y'ibicurane byitwa gutoranya neza.
Dukurikije isesengura ryakozwe hagati y'ibinyabuzima bya SARS-CoVs by'abantu n'inyamaswa, SARS-CoV bivugwa ko yihutira kumenyera aho ikorera, cyane cyane mu guhinduranya kwa RDB muri poroteyine ya S.
Ubusanzwe, RBD mu poroteyine ya S ya CoV ifitanye isano n'ubudahangarwa kandi itoranywa cyane n'abasirikare b'umubiri mu gice cy'umubiri cy'iyo virusi.
Muri SARS-CoV, RBD iri mu bwoko bwa amino acide 318 kugeza 510 kuri S1 fragment, ifata ACE2 mu bantu ndetse n'ibindi binyabuzima.
RBD ya SARS-CoV ishobora kwanduza ACE2 mu nyamaswa zitandukanye, harimo impara, inguge, imbeba n'imbwa, bityo ikemurira virusi ikwirakwira mu moko atandukanye.
Mu by'ukuri, ibisigisigi 6 bya amino acide byabonetse bitandukanye n'ibyabonetse mu bantu mu gihe RBD yari ifite ibisigazwa 4 byabonetse mu bwoko bwa ACE2.
SARS-CoV nshya ifite ihinduka ry'imiterere ya K479N na S487T RBD, bishobora kongera ubufatanye bwa poroteyine ya spike na ACE2 ikoreshwa n'abantu.
Ni ukuvuga ko za aside ebyiri za amino zishobora kugira uruhare rukomeye mu gutuma abantu bahangana n'indwara.
Ni ngombwa kumenya ko SARS-CoV-2 ifite ubwandu bw'indwara nk'ubwa SARS-CoV.
Itandukaniro ry'ibice 30% hagati ya SARS-CoV-2 na SARS-CoV ku rwego rwa S1 rwa poroteyine ya S, bivuga ko ifitanye isano ya hafi na poroteyine ya S na ACE2 mu bantu ishobora kuba yahindutse.
Mu by'ukuri, ubushakashatsi bwa cryo-EM bugaragaza isano iri hagati ya 10 na 20 ikomeye muri iyi ngamba kurusha ACE2 mu bantu na poroteyine ya SARS-CoV S.
Bizashimisha kandi kureba niba ubundi buryo bwo kwanduzanya bushobora gukenerwa mu gukwirakwiza SARS-CoV-2.
Igishishikaje ni uko HCoV-NL63 nayo itera ACE2 imbaraga ariko ikoresheje undi muti wa S.
Hariho izindi HCoV nyinshi, zirimo aminopeptidase N kuri HCoV-229E, na 9-O-acetylated sialic acid kuri HCoV-OC43.
Bishobora kandi gusobanura uburyo virusi ya CoV ikora neza mu bantu nyuma yo gukwirakwira mu bwoko butandukanye bitewe n'inyamaswa ikuriramo.
Uretse kuba HCoV ifite ubwandu bw'indwara z'ibyorezo, uburyo ikwirakwira mu bwoko butandukanye bugengwa n'ibindi bintu bitandukanye bitewe n'aho ikorera n'uburyo ikwirakwira.
Itandukaniro ry'indwara z'indwara hagati y'abantu n'ibindi biremwa byanduza HCoVs nk'imbeba, ingamiya n'imbeba bishobora kuba inzitizi mu kwanduzanya indwara mu bwoko butandukanye.
HCoVs zinyura mu gice cy'umubiri cy'indwara kandi zikirinda inzitizi z'umubiri kubera ko zikwirakwiza neza indwara mu bwoko butandukanye.
Bityo rero, imyanzuro ya molekile muri icyo gice cy'ingenzi cy'umubiri w'agakoko ngengabuzima ntikiramenyekana.
Gushakisha genome yose ku buryo butagira aho bushingiye, hakoreshejwe ikoranabuhanga rigezweho, bishobora gutanga umusaruro.
HCoVs z'igihe kirekire zitamenyekanye: gusubira mu ntangiriro
Ihinduka ry'ubwoko bwa CoVs zituruka ku mikorobe ritanga amahirwe menshi mu kuvuka kwa HCoVs zitari zisanzwe zizwi.
Muri ubwo buryo, CoV y'impanga ikora nk'isoko y'ibinyabuzima bya HCoVs.
Byongeye kandi, ihinduka ry'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima n'ihindagurika ry'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima na byo bigena uko HCoV ikura kandi bigira uruhare runini mu iterambere ry'iyo virusi.
Urugero, kugira cyangwa kubura imiterere y'ingirabuzima fatizo z'ingirabuzima fatizo zitagira icyo zivugaho bishobora guhindura imiterere y'ingirabuzima fatizo.
Muri poroteyine z'inyongera za SARS-CoV, ORF8 ifatwa nk'ifite uruhare rukomeye mu kumenyekanisha abantu, kuko virusi ya SARS-CoV y'imbeba yatandukanyijwe ariko igasanga ifite poroteyine zitandukanye za ORF8.
Ikimenyetso cyo gusenyuka kwa nucleotide 29 cya SARS-CoVs cyabonetse mu bimenyetso byatoranyijwe mu ntangiriro z'indwara muri muntu.
Iri koranabuhanga ritandukanya ORF8 n'izindi ORF8a na ORF8b kandi ritekereza ko ari ihinduka ry'imiterere rituma habaho impinduka mu mibereho y'udukoko.
Byongeye kandi, SARS-CoV ifite amateka y'ubushobozi bwo kwihuza mu bwoko bwa alpha- na gamma-CoVs, byerekanwa n'umubare muto w'ubwiyongere mu RNA-dependent RNA polymerase.
Ibice bimwe na bimwe by'ubufatanye byerekanwe muri nsp9, cyane cyane muri nsp10, hamwe n'ibice bya nsp14.
Mu buryo nk'ubwo, byemejwe ko mu ntangiriro z'icyorezo cya MERS-CoV hari ubwandu bw'ingamiya muri Arabiya Sawudite.
Uretse SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, hari izindi HCoVs zisanzwe zifite ubwandu bw'ubwoko butandukanye, aho HCoVs zifatanya na CoVs z'inyamaswa mu buryo bw'imiterere.
