Ariko kandi, si ibintu by'impanuka ko HCoVs zitigeze zimenyekana zigaragara mu myaka 20 ishize.
CoVs ntizitera indwara cyangwa ngo zitere ibimenyetso byoroheje mu bikurura nk'ibicurane cyangwa ingamiya.
Iyo ndwara ishobora kwibasira cyane umuntu, ariko ntiyitume arwara indwara.
Icyo ni cyo gituma indwara zitandura zidakurikizwa n'abantu, zituma abantu bahura n'indwara zangiza.
Ibimenyetso by'uburwayi ni byinshi cyane bitewe n'ibicurane by'ibicurane by'ibinyabutabire (cytokine storm) ku buryo uko uburwayi buba bukomeye, ni na ko ibyago byo kwangirika kw'ibihaha bigenda byiyongera.
Ugereranyije n'abantu badafite ibimenyetso, udukoko turinda kwanduzanya na CoV.
Ubwo buryo bwo kuvura indwara z'ibicurane bushobora kuba ingirakamaro mu kuvura SARS-CoV-2.
Interferon ikora cyane mu biheri.
Ku bw'ibyo, uburyo bwo guhangana na interféron yo mu bwoko bwa I byibuze igihe SARS-CoV-2 imaze kugaragara mu bantu bugomba kuba bufite ingaruka nziza.
Mu buryo nk'ubwo, gutera ingufu NLRP3 mu gitsina ntibigira ingaruka nziza.
Muri ubwo buryo, guhagarika NLRP3 inflammasome hamwe na MCC950 bishobora gufasha mu kuvura COVID-19.
Icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 gikurikiza inzira imwe ya SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV.
Nubwo beta-CoV yagaragaye ko ifite 95% by'udupira tw'ingirabuzima fatizo na SARS-CoV, hari kandi CoV ya Kvirus ifite 96% by'udupira tw'ingirabuzima fatizo na SARS-CoV-2.
Ariko kandi, inyamaswa z'inkazi n'izindi zigurishwa mu masoko zisanzwe zisanzwe zifite virusi zisa na SARS-CoV, zikaba zisanzwe zisanzwe zanduza SARS-CoV-2 mbere yuko zivugwa.
Pangolin beta-CoVs yagaragaye ifite aho ihuriye na SARS-CoV-2, ibyo bikaba byerekana ko pangolin ishobora kuba ifite ubwandu bw'indwara cyangwa se pangolin beta-CoVs ishobora kuba ifite imiterere y'ingirabuzima fatizo itera SARS-CoV-2 mu buryo bw'imiterere ya nyuma.
Nubwo ibibazo bikiriho, nta bimenyetso bigaragaza ko SARS-CoV-2 yakorewe ku bushake cyangwa se ko yakozwe n'abantu.
CoVs zagiye zigabanuka mu bantu kubera icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 cyabanje.
Ubushakashatsi ku mikorobe n'ibindi bikoko bya CoVs byahinduye mu buryo bwihuse uburyo bwo gusobanukirwa uruhare rw'indwara z'inyamaswa n'iz'inyamaswa zifite HCoVs mu kwanduza abantu.
Amakuru akomeye yerekana ko SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 zituruka mu mibu kandi ko zikwirakwira mu bantu binyuze mu binyabuzima byanduye.
Kubera ko SARS-CoV iterwa n'abantu bahura n'ibiheri mu masoko, gufunga amasoko acuruza ibikomoka ku bimera no kwica ibiheri byafasha mu guhashya icyorezo cya SARS.
Mu buryo nk'ubwo, ingona zigomba guhagarikwa ku isoko ry'ibikomoka ku bimera kuko zifite ubushobozi bwo kurwanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara z'inyamaswa ku bantu, hagamijwe gutahura ubwoko butandukanye bwa beta-CoVs z'ingona zirwanya cyane SARS-CoV-2.
Icyakora, niba SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kwanduzwa n'abantu binyuze mu nyamaswa z'ibinyamanswa n'izindi nyamaswa zimeze nk'abantu n'uburyo ishobora kwanduzwa bizagaragazwa mu bushakashatsi buzakurikiraho.
Ku rundi ruhande, MERS-CoV imaze igihe kirekire mu ngamiya.
Ingamiya ni ingenzi mu ngendo, kandi ni zo zitanga inyama, amata, amasaro n'ubwoya.
Ni ubwoko bw'ibinyamushongo buzwi cyane mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati no muri Afurika.
Ubu noneho biragoye cyane kwica ingamiya zose kubera urukingo rwa MERS, rwakozwe mu masoko y'inyamaswa zo mu mashyamba yo mu Bushinwa mu rwego rwo gukumira ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2.
Kugira ngo hatagira icyorezo cya MERS kiza, urukingo rw'iyi ndwara rugomba gukorwaho urukingo rwa MERS-CoV rw'ingamiya, rufatanyije n'izindi nzego z'ubuvuzi.
Kubera ko nta cyo twakora ngo turwanye iyo mikorobe, ishobora guhinduka ikongera igatera indi.
Ubwoko butandukanye bwa CoV butera indwara zituruka ku nyamaswa zijya ku bantu bwagaragaye mu ishyamba.
By'umwihariko, ni CoV ya virusi ifite ubushobozi bwo gukwirakwiza indwara kuva ku ngurube kugeza ku bantu mu byiciro byinshi.
Hari amahirwe menshi ko CoV zitwara indwara zinyura mu nyamaswa zijya ku bantu zitagaragaye bitewe n'uko habonetse CoV nshya zitwara vuba kandi/cyangwa mu bantu.
Imigenzo yo kurya inyamaswa zo mu gasozi mu bice bimwe na bimwe by'u Bushinwa igomba gucibwa kugira ngo abantu n'inyamaswa badakomeza guhura bidakenewe.
Mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya SARS, MERS na COVID-19, gutegura neza no guhangana nacyo birakenewe.
Mu by'ukuri, hari mikorobe nyinshi zimaze imyaka ibarirwa mu bihumbi ziri ku isi.
Iyo ibonye uburyo, iguma mu karere k'ubutaka ikaguruka.
Nubwo ibivumvuri bifite ubushobozi bwo gukwirakwiza mikorobe, abantu bashobora kugabanya amahirwe yo guhura n'ibivumvuri n'ibindi biremwa byo mu gasozi iyo abantu babwiwe ko bagomba kubyirinda.
Ubushakashatsi buhoraho burakenewe ku bantu bafite ibyago byo kwandura kubera ko gusobanukirwa neza imiterere ya CoVs hamwe n'ibinyabuzima by'ibinyabuzima bizagaragara ko bifite akamaro mu kurwanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara z'inyamaswa-ku-bantu ndetse no mu gihe kizaza.
Mu gusoza, uburyo bwiza bwo kwirinda ko indwara z'inyamaswa zinyura mu bantu ni abantu, aho usanga hari uturemangingo tw'ibinyabuzima dutuma indwara z'inyamaswa zinyura mu bantu.
Hari byinshi bitaramenyekana ku nkomoko y'indwara ya SARS-CoV-2 yandurira mu bantu.
Mbere na mbere, niba ibivumvuri bitanga virusi itera SARS-CoV-2 mu bivumvuri, ni ngombwa kureba uko ibivumvuri n'ibivumvuri bihuza mu bice byabo.
Icya kabiri, niba udukoko dukwirakwiza indwara mu bantu, ubwo uburyo abantu bakwirakwiza indwara bugomba kwitabwaho.
Icya gatatu, niba inyamaswa imeze nk'umuntu ikora nk'aho ari ahantu hatangirira mikorobe, uburyo itari kumwe n'izindi nyamaswa harimo abantu, udukoko n'ibinyamanswa, bigomba gusobanurwa.
Amaherezo, kubera ko inyamaswa nyinshi zimeze nk'abantu harimo n'amatungo ashobora kwandura SARS-CoV-2, hakenewe ubugenzuzi no gupimwa.
Niba ari urukwavu, ingunzu cyangwa ikindi gikoko gisa n'umuntu, birashoboka ko SARS-CoV-2 cyangwa izindi virusi ziterwa n'indwara zisa cyane na zo zizagaragara mu gace k'ibinyabuzima by'ubwoko bwazo.
Ubushakashatsi burambuye kuri iki kibazo buzatanga ibisobanuro ku buryo virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 ikora mu nyamaswa, harimo n'ingaruka nziza ku gukumira no gukumira COVID-19 mu bantu.
Gushyira mu buryo ibisabwa kugira ngo umurwayi ukekwaho  n'uwari wemejwe ko afite COVID-19 yemewe , ni ngombwa
Ku ya 6 Gashyantare 2020, itsinda ryacu ryasohoye amabwiriza yihuse yo gupima no kuvura abantu banduye coronavirus nshya ya 2019 (2019-nCoV), kandi ayo mabwiriza agaragaza ubuhanga bwacu no kwerekana uburyo bwiza bwo kurwanya icyorezo ku isi.
Nyamara, icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) ni icyorezo gishya, ubumenyi dufite kuricyo bugenda bwiyongera bitewe n'ibyagezweho mu bushakashatsi bukomeje gukorwa n'uburyo bwo kugivura; bityo rero, uburyo bwo gupima no kugivura bugenda buhinduka.
Muri iyi baruwa, twashubije ikibazo kimwe ku mabwiriza yacu kandi dutanga amabwiriza agezweho mu gufata icyemezo cy'ibikoresho by'ubushakashatsi n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi bishingiye ku mabwiriza ya vuba y'igeragezwa n'ivurwa rya COVID-19 (Inyigisho y'ibanze y'igishoro n'ivura rya COVID-19 (verisiyo ya karindwi)) yemejwe na Komite y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima ya Repubulika y'Abashinwa.
Mu Ukuboza 2019, icyorezo cya 2019 novel coronavirus (2019-nCoV) cyateje icyorezo, ubu cyitwa coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19) kandi cyanduye virusi yitwa severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, OMS yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo cy'indwara ku isi.
Mu rwego rwo kurwanya SARS-CoV-2, itsinda ryacu ryateguye ibyangombwa byihutirwa byashyizwe kuri interineti muri Military Medical Research ku ya 06 Gashyantare 2020.
Kuva icyo gitabo cyasohoka, abantu benshi baragikunze.
Ariko birakwiriye ko tumenya ko COVID-19 ari indwara nshya, ubumenyi dufite kuri yo bugenda bwiyongera bitewe n'ibyagezweho mu bushakashatsi bukomeje gukorwa n'uburyo bwo kuyivura; bityo rero, uburyo bwo gupima no kuvura bugenda buhinduka.
Ibikorwa byo gupima no kuvura COVID-19 byakozwe na Komite y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima ya Repubulika y'Abashinwa (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/), hagati ya 16 Mutarama 2020 na 3 Werurwe 2020, byasohoye impapuro zirindwi z'ibanze z'ibanze.
Ibyacu byasobanuwe na Zhou na bagenzi be, bateguye uburyo bworoshye bwo gupima bushingiye ku bimenyetso by'ubuvuzi.
Umurimo wabo watumye turushaho gushimangira imyizerere yacu kandi utuma turushaho kumenya ko iki kibazo cyugarije isi yose.
Tugomba kubashimira kandi tukabashimira umurimo wabo mwiza.
Ariko kandi, imirimo yabo ikeneye kuvugururwa hakurikijwe amabwiriza mashya yo gupima no kuvura COVID-19 (Icyiciro cya karindwi) n'ubushakashatsi bushya.
Nk'uko byemejwe n'ibyavuzwe ku ncuro ya karindwi (3 Werurwe 2020), kwemeza umurwayi ukekwaho indwara bisaba guhuza kimwe mu bintu bibiri by'ingenzi bijyanye n'amateka y'uburwayi n'ibipimo by'ubuvuzi by'ibitaro kugira ngo haboneke umwanzuro wa nyuma, cyangwa bisaba kuzuza ibipimo bitatu by'ubuvuzi mu gihe nta mateka y'uburwayi asobanutse:
Amateka y'ubwandu: (1) kuba waragiye cyangwa warigeze kuba mu mujyi wa Wuhan n'uturere tuwukikije, cyangwa mu tundi duce tw'isi twabonetsemo COVID-19 mu minsi 14 mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira kugaragara; (2) kuba warigeze kuba uri hafi y'abantu barwaye SARS-CoV-2 (mu gihe cy'igerageza rya aside ya nucleic nziza); (3) kuba warigeze kuba hafi y'abarwaye malariya cyangwa abafite ibibazo byo guhumeka baturutse mu mujyi wa Wuhan n'uturere tuwukikije, cyangwa mu tundi duce twabonetsemo COVID-19 mu minsi 14 mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira kugaragara; (4) kuba warigeze kuba hafi y'abarwayi bagaragaye (abarwayi 2 bafite malariya na/cyangwa barwaye muri iki cyumweru bazaba baragaragaye mu bigo by'indembe, mu biro by'ubucuruzi, mu bigo by'amashuri, mu matsinda, mu bigo by'amashuri, mu bigo by'indembe).
Ibimenyetso by'uburwayi: (1) umuriro n'/cyangwa guhumeka nabi; (2) ibimenyetso by'ubwandu bwa COVID-19; (3) ingirabuzima fatizo zera z'amaraso zigaragaza ko ingirabuzima fatizo z'amaraso ari nziza cyangwa zifite umubare muto w'ingirabuzima fatizo z'amaraso mu gihe cy'imboneko.
Kwipimisha bigomba gukorwa ku murwayi ukekwaho ubwandu cyangwa ibipimo bya PCR bikurikira: (1) ibizamini bya PCR byerekana ko umuntu afite SARS-CoV-2; (2) ukurikirana kwa virusi yose ya virusi bigaragaza ko umuntu afite coronavirus nshya; (3) ibizamini bya plasma bigaragaza ko umuntu afite IgM antibody na IgG antibody by'umwihariko kurwanya SARS-CoV-2; cyangwa ihinduka rya IgG antibody ya SARS-CoV-2 kuva kuri negative ikajya kuri positive, cyangwa se kuzamuka kwa titer ≥4 inshuro mu gihe cyo gukira kurusha mu gihe cyo kurwara.
Turabona ko ibizamini bya PCR byihuse byo kubona aside ya nucleic mu musarani cyangwa mu maraso byongerewe ku nomero ya kabiri (18 Mutarama 2020) na 22 Mutarama 2020.
Ibipimo by'amaraso byongewemo ibimenyetso by'ubwandu ku itariki ya kane (27 Mutarama 2020) na gatanu (8 Gashyantare 2020); naho ibimenyetso by'ibipimo by'amazi yo mu mubiri byongewemo ibimenyetso ku itariki ya karindwi.
Ihinduka rishingiye ku bushakashatsi bwo gushaka uburyo bwo gupima aside ya nucleic mu buryo bwihuse, hamwe n'ibipimo by'amaraso bivuye mu isuzuma ry'amaraso, byongereye ubushobozi bwo gupima ibipimo bitandukanye, kandi byashyigikiye ko abarwayi bagira abasirikare b'umubiri ubwabo nk'ibanze mu kwemeza umurwayi.
Ikindi kandi, hari ibindi bintu byinshi bigaragaza ko tugomba kwitondera abarwayi batagaragaza ibimenyetso bidasanzwe.
Ku bw'ibyo, ikarita ya Zhou na bagenzi be ikwiriye gusubirwamo, kuko yagaragaje umuntu udafite ibimenyetso by'indwara afite amahirwe make (ibyago bike) .
Iyi gahunda y'amanota ikeneye kandi kwemezwa mu bindi bigo by'ubuvuzi n'ubushakashatsi.
Mu magambo make, twiringiye ko hari ibindi bihamya bifatika bizagaragara kandi dutera abasomyi inkunga yo kubivugaho.
Kubera ko tuzi neza icyo Imana yateganyije kandi tukamenya n'icyo tugomba gukora, dufatira ingamba zo gukurikiza amategeko y'amahanga yacu.
Itsinda ryacu rizasubiramo ibyangombwa byacu ku gihe kugira ngo bifashe.
Bangladesh yatangaje ko abandi bantu batanu bapfuye bishwe na COVID-19, umubare munini w'abapfa ku munsi
Ejo, Bangladesh yemeje ko abandi bantu batanu bapfuye kuri uwo munsi bishwe na COVID-19.
Ni umubare munini w'abantu bapfuye ku munsi umwe bishwe n'iyi virusi.
Kugeza ejo, Ikigo cya Bangladesh gishinzwe iby'indwara z'ibyorezo, kurwanya indwara n'ubushakashatsi (IEDCR) cyanditse abarwayi 114 n'abakize 33 bari mu rugo.
Abantu 17 ni bo bapfuye.
Mu itangazo ryashyizwe ku rubuga rwa interineti, umukozi wa IEDCR, Dr Meerjady Sabrina Flora, yavuze ko abapfuye ari abagabo bane n'umugore umwe.
Nk'uko Dr Meerjady abivuga, babiri mu bapfuye bari mu kigero cy'imyaka 60, babiri bari hagati y'imyaka 51 na 60, naho umwe yari hagati y'imyaka 41 na 50.
Yongeyeho ko babiri muri bo bakomoka i Dhaka.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo ku isi.
Umuyobozi w'ibitaro yabwiye ikigo cy'itangazamakuru cya Anadolu ko mu bapfuye harimo Jalal Saifur Rahman, umukozi wa Komisiyo yo kurwanya ruswa ya Bengali, wari urwariye mu bitaro bya Kuwait Maitree.
Ku wa gatandatu, Minisitiri w'ubwikorezi muri Bangladesh Obaidul Quader yatangaje mu itangazo rya videwo ko ingendo zose z'indege zizahagarikwa igihe kirekire kurusha uko byari biteganyijwe, kugeza ku wa gatandatu utaha.
Ihagarikwa ry'ingendo ryatangiye ku ya 26 Werurwe kandi ryari rigomba kurangira ku ya 4 Mata.
Ingendo z'ibintu by'ibanze - imiti, peteroli n'ibiribwa - zari zikirekuriwe.
Abarwayi ba mbere ba COVID-19 muri Bangladesh bagaragaye ku ya 8 Werurwe, ni abantu babiri bagarutse muri icyo gihugu baturutse mu Butaliyani n'umugore w'umwe muri abo bantu.
Ku itariki ya 19 Werurwe, abo bagabo uko ari batatu bari bakize.
SARS-CoV-2 imaze guhitana abantu miliyoni imwe ku isi
Ku wa Kane, umubare w'abarwayi ba SARS-CoV-2 coronavirus warenze miliyoni ku isi nk'uko byatangajwe na Johns Hopkins University.
Abantu bagera ku bihumbi 52 nibo bamaze kumenyekana ko bishwe na COVID-19, icyorezo cy'indwara ya coronavirus.
Ibi byakozwe ku munsi umwe Malawi yemeje umurwayi wayo wa mbere na Zambia yemeje umuntu umwe wapfuye azize coronavirus.
Koreya ya Ruguru yatangaje ku wa Kane ko ari kimwe mu bihugu byasigaye bitaratewe n'icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Ku gicamunsi cyo kuri uyu wa Kane, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko hari abarwayi 1,051,635 barimo 79,332 bakingiwe mu masaha 24 atarenze saa yine za mu gitondo, ku isaha yo mu Burayi bwo hagati (0800 UTC) ku ya 4 Mata.
Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, abantu basaga 244.000 barwaye indwara z'ibyorezo, kandi abagera ku 5.900 barapfuye.
CBS News yavuze ko Kaminuza ya Johns Hopkins yavuze ko muri Amerika hari abantu barenga 1.000 bapfuye ku wa Gatatu bishwe na coronavirus.
Ku isi hose, ibihugu byatangaje ko bizashyiraho ingamba zikomeye zo kwirinda indwara.
Ku wa Kane, Sergei Sobyanin, umuyobozi w'umujyi wa Moscou, yongereye igihe cyo gufunga umujyi kugeza ku ya 1 Gicurasi.
Mu gihugu hose, Perezida Vladimir Putin yatangaje ko Abarusiya bazishyurwa nubwo bataza ku kazi kugeza ku ya 30 Mata.
Inteko ishinga amategeko ya Portugal yateye utwatsi icyemezo cyo kongera iminsi 15 y'igifungo cy'akazi, abenshi mu bantu 215 barabyemeye, 10 barabyamagana, kandi nta n'umwe wabyemeye.
Arabiya Sawudite yongereye igihe cyo kunywa ikawa mu mijyi yera ya Mecca na Medina ku munsi wose; mbere, ikawa yabaga hagati ya saa cyenda z'umugoroba na saa kumi n'ebyiri za mu gitondo.
Thailand yateganyije ikawa hagati ya saa yine z'ijoro na saa kumi z'ijoro.
Guverineri wa Ohio, Mike DeWine, yatangaje ko leta yongereye amasaha yo kuguma mu rugo kugeza ku ya 1 Gicurasi.
