Ku wa Gatatu, Woolworths na yo yagabanyije ibiciro by'ibikoresho byo kugura no kohereza mu rugo ku munsi.
Izi mpinduka zikurikiraho kugabanya inshuro enye ku isoko ryatanzwe na Woolworths na Coles ku ya 4 na 5 Werurwe muri izo sosiyete zombi.
Mu ibaruwa Coles yanditse ku ya 8 Werurwe, yavuze ko amategeko y'ubucuruzi akomeje gufatwa, "amaduka menshi arangiza mu isaha imwe gusa yo kuyatanga", avuga ko ibyo bikenewe bitigeze bibaho, naho ALDI, yanditse kuri Facebook ku wa Kabiri yavuze ko "bitari byitezwe".
Ubucuruzi bwazamutse cyane mu cyumweru gishize nk'uko bivugwa n'umuvugizi wa Woolworths.
Iguriro rya Costco i Canberra na ryo ryashyizeho ibipimo byemewe ku bicuruzwa bibiri mu cyumweru gishize.
Kugira ngo Coles abone ibyangombwa by'ibanze, yasabye abakozi gukora imirimo myinshi kandi y'inyongera, Woolworths na yo yasaba ko bahabwa ibindi bintu, naho ALDI yo ibaha ibindi nk'uko yari yabiteganyije ku wa Gatatu w'ibyumweru by'umwihariko.
Russell Zimmerman, umuyobozi w'ishyirahamwe ry'abacuruzi b'ibikoresho byo mu nzu muri Australia, yavuze ko abacuruzi bagerageza kongera ibicuruzwa byabo ariko ko kuba abayobozi bahagaritse imodoka nyinshi cyane ari ikibazo.
Yiteze ko amafaranga azakoreshwa yiyongera, kuko abakozi bagerageza guhuza ibyifuzo n'iminsi mike.
Ku wa kabiri, ALDI yatangaje ko nyuma yo gushyira hanze ibicuruzwa by'ihindagurika, amaduka amwe na amwe atazashobora gukora ibitaragenze neza ku wa gatatu.
Mu nkuru yatanzwe na News.com.au, Dr Gary Mortimer, impuguke mu bucuruzi bw'ibikoresho by'ibanze byo muri kaminuza ya Queensland y'ikoranabuhanga, yavuze ko amaduka atuma abantu bagurisha buri joro.
Yavuze ko izo nyoni ziba nini cyane, bigatuma ibicuruzwa biba bike, ku buryo iyo bicitse, ibitunguru biba byinshi cyane, bigatuma abantu bumva ko hari ibyangiritse.
Russell Zimmerman yabwiye ABC News ati "Coles na Woolworths batekereza ko [iyo] ibicuruzwa byinshi, urugero nk'ibikoresho byo gusukura intoki n'ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki, biboneka mu buryo bwinshi, ibyo bicuruzwa bishobora kugabanya ibicuruzwa bitangirika".
Ku wa Gatatu, umwe mu bakoreraga mu rugo rw'intama, yavuze ko nta zindi ntama zari zihari.
Kimberly-Clark, ikora imyenda, na Solaris Paper ikora Sorbent, bemeje ko bakora amasaha 24 n'amasaha 7 kugira ngo bahangane n'ibikenewe, nk'uko bitangazwa na News.com.au.
Urubuga Domain.com, rukora ibicuruzwa by'imitungo, rwatangaje ko hari abacuruzi batanga ibishyimbo ku buntu ku watsinze igitego cya mbere cya Melbourne, mu gihe hari ibicuruzwa bike kubera ko abaguzi bari mu kiruhuko mu mpera z'icyumweru kirekire kirimo n'umunsi w'umurimo.
Mu itangazo ryo kuwa kane ry'ikinyamakuru cya NT News, ikinyamakuru cya buri munsi cy'i Darwin, hari harimo igitabo cy'ibitabo umunani cyagombaga gukurwaho kigakoreshwa nk'ibikoresho byo gucururizamo.
Amaduka yabanje kwanga gushyiraho ibihano, nk'uko byavuzwe na ABC Australia ku ya 3 Werurwe aho yavuze ko nta gahunda yo gushyiraho ibihano ku bicuruzwa.
Russell Zimmerman yongeyeho ko hari n'ibindi bicuruzwa biri ku isoko, harimo udupfukamunwa, ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki, ibiryo byumye, isabune n'ibikoresho byo gusukura intoki.
Mu buryo nk'ubwo, hanze ya Australia, ku Cyumweru nimugoroba, isoko ryo kuri interineti rya Ocado ryagaragaye rihagarika kugura udukingirizo tw'ubwoko bwa Andres, aho umuntu agura hagati ya 2 na 12 tw'ubwoko bwa Andres.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo ku isi
Ku wa Gatatu, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko icyorezo cya COVID-19  cyatewe na coronavirus SARS-CoV-2  ari icyorezo ku isi.
Nubwo ijambo "icyorezo ku isi" ryerekeza gusa ku buryo indwara ikwirakwira, aho kwerekeza ku buryo indwara zimwe na zimwe zifite ubukana, OMS yavuze ko ubutegetsi bugomba gufata ingamba:
"Ibihugu byose bishobora guhindura uko iki cyorezo cyugarije isi yose.
Ibihugu bigomba kugenzura, gupima, kuvura, gutandukanya, gukurikirana no gukusanya abantu kuri iki kibazo", ni amagambo yavuzwe n'Umuyobozi Mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus.
"Turababajwe cyane n'uko iki cyorezo cyandura kandi ko kirangwa n'ubukana kandi ko kititabwaho".
Dukurikije uko Dr. Tom Frieden wahoze ari umuyobozi w'Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika Gishinzwe Kurwanya Indwara (CDC) yabivuze, icyo cyorezo "nticyari cyitezwe".
Mu itangazo ryasohowe na CNN mu kwezi kwa kabiri, yagize ati "uretse iyi, nta kindi cyorezo cy'indwara y'ubuhumekero cyigeze kigaragara kuva cyaduka kugeza aho cyakwirakwiriye ku isi".
Ghebreyesus yagize igitekerezo nk'icyo, avuga ko "nta kindi gihe twigeze tubona icyorezo cy'icyorezo cya coronavirus".
Yongeyeho ati "nta n'ubwo tubona ko icyo ari ikibazo cy'ingutu kizakemuka ku isi hose".
Icyiciro gishya cy'icyorezo cy'isi cyaje nyuma y'icyemezo cy'ishami rya OMS mu kwezi kwa mbere cyo gutangaza ko iki cyorezo ari ikibazo cy'ubuzima bw'abantu ku isi.
Umuyobozi w'Ikigo cy'Igihugu cya Amerika Gishinzwe Indwara z'Ibitera Mbonera n'Indwara Zandura, Dr. Anthony Fauci, yavuze ko iki cyorezo "kizatera indwara zidakwirakwizwa".
Ku wa kane, Associated Press yatangaje ko hari nibura abarwayi 126,000 ba COVID-19 ku isi, muri bo 4.600 barapfuye.
Icyorezo cya coronavirus 201920 ni icyorezo gikomeje cy'indwara ya COVID-19 iterwa na virusi itera indwara y'ubuhumekero ikomeye (SARS-CoV-2).
Iki cyorezo cyamenyekanye i Wuhan, mu Bushinwa, mu Ukuboza 2019, gitangazwa nk'icyorezo cy'indwara ku bantu ku ya 30 Mutarama 2020, ndetse gitangazwa nk'icyorezo ku isi ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020.
Kugeza ku ya 10 Mata 2020, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 1.61 banduye COVID-19 bari bamaze kumenyekana mu bihugu 210 n'ahantu hatandukanye, kandi hapfuye abantu bagera ku 97.000.
Abantu bagera ku 364.000 barokotse.
Umubare w'abandura bapfa ugereranywa na 4% mu Bushinwa, mu gihe ku isi hose ni 13.04% muri Algeria na .08% muri Nouvelle Zélande.
