Abashinzwe ubuzima mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu Bushinwa (umurwa mukuru w'intara ya Hubei) batangaje ko hari abantu bake banduye icyorezo kitaramenyekana kuva ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, kandi ko iperereza ryatangiye mu ntangiriro za Mutarama 2020.
Abanduye bagaragaye bahuye n'ibicuruzwa byo mu nyanja byo mu isoko rya Huanan (Seafood Wholesale Market) bityo virusi bivugwa ko yaturutse ku nyamaswa igera ku bantu.
Virusi yateye iki cyorezo yitwa SARS-CoV-2, ni virusi iherutse kuvumburwa ifite aho ihuriye n'indwara z'imbeba zitwa coronaviruses, pangolin coronaviruses na SARS-CoV. Umuntu wa mbere wanduye iyi virusi yaje kumenyekana nyuma y'aho ku ya 1 Ukuboza 2019, kandi ntaho yagaragaye ko yahuye n'ibicurane by'ibikomoka ku binure.
Mu barwayi ba mbere batangajwe mu Ukuboza 2019, bibiri bya gatatu by'abo barwayi bagaragaye ko bafitanye isano n'isoko.
Ku ya 13 Werurwe 2020, ikinyamakuru South China Morning Post cyatangaje ko umuntu w'imyaka 55 w'imyaka 55 w'imyaka 17 y'amavuko wo mu ntara ya Hubei, ashobora kuba ari we wa mbere wanduye. Ku ya 26 Gashyantare 2020, OMS yatangaje ko mu gihe abarwayi bashya bari bagabanutse mu Bushinwa ariko bakomeza kwiyongera mu Butaliyani, Irani na Koreya y'Epfo, umubare w'abarwayi bashya hanze y'Ubushinwa warenze uw'abarwayi bashya mu Bushinwa ku nshuro ya mbere.
Hari igihe umubare nyawo w'abarwayi ushobora kuba utari wavuzwe, cyane cyane abafite ibimenyetso byoroheje.
Ku ya 26 Gashyantare, umubare muto w'abarwayi bagaragaye mu rubyiruko ruri munsi y'imyaka 19 ni ukuvuga 2.4% by'abarwayi bose ku isi. Umujyanama mukuru w'ubushakashatsi mu by'ubuvuzi mu Bwongereza, Patrick Vallance, yavuze ko 60% by'abaturage bo mu Bwongereza bashobora kwandura mbere y'uko icyorezo kigaragara mu baturage.
Abarwayi ni umubare w'abantu bose basuzumwe bagasanga bafite COVID-19, kandi bagaragaweho ubwandu bushingiye ku bipimo byemewe.
Ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu na kimwe cyari gifite abaturage barenga 3%, kandi ibihugu byinshi bifite gahunda yo kutagira ibipimo by'abantu bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje, nk'u Butaliyani, u Buholandi, Esipanye n'u Busuwisi.
Ubushakashatsi bwashyizwe ahagaragara ku ya 16 Werurwe bwagaragaje ko mu Bushinwa, kugeza ku ya 23 Mutarama, abagera kuri 86% by'abarwayi batarahabwa urukingo, kandi ko abarwayi batarahabwa urukingo ari bo bakoreshaga 79% by'abahawe urukingo.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku itariki ya 30 Werurwe bwagaragaje ko umubare w'abanduye mu Butaliyani warutaga kure cyane uwo wari watangajwe mbere.
Ubushakashatsi bwa mbere bwagaragaje ko umubare w'ibyago (R0) bya COVID-19 ari 1.4 kugeza kuri 2.4.
Ikigo cyo muri Amerika Gishinzwe Kurwanya Indwara n'Ubuvuzi cyavuze ko uwo mubare ushobora kuba uri hagati ya 5.7 na 5.7.
Abenshi mu barwayi ba COVID-19 barakira.
Ku bantu barembye, igihe kuva ibimenyetso bitangira kugaragara kugeza ku rupfu kiri hagati y'iminsi 6 na 41, ariko ni cyo kiruta ku bantu bose uko ari 14.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, abantu bagera ku 97,000 baramaze kwicwa na COVID-19.
