Umubare nyawo w'abapfa bazize COVID-19 ushobora kuba uri hejuru cyane kuko ushobora kuba utari umubare w'abapfa batabanje gupimwa - haba mu rugo, mu bigo byita ku bageze mu za bukuru n'ahandi.
Amakuru y'akarere aturuka mu Butaliyani yagaragaje ko umubare w'abapfuye mu gihe cy'icyorezo warenze inshuro 4-5 umubare w'abamaze kwandura COVID.
Umuvugizi w'ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) yemeye ko "tuzi ko [imibare y'abapfuye] idasobanutse neza", ibyo twabemeje binyuze mu gutanga inama ku baturage bo muri Amerika.
Umuntu wa mbere wapfuye hanze y'Ubushinwa yapfuye ku ya 1 Gashyantare muri Filipine, naho uwa mbere wapfuye hanze ya Aziya yapfuye ku ya 14 Gashyantare mu Bufaransa.
Ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare, hanze y'u Bushinwa, abantu basaga 12 bapfiriye muri buri gihugu, Iran, Koreya y'Epfo n'u Butaliyani.
Ku ya 13 Werurwe, ibihugu n'uturere birenga 40 byatangaje ko abantu bapfuye ku migabane hafi ya yose uretse Antarctica.
Ibipimo bihinduka bitewe n'akarere n'ibihe bitandukanye kandi biterwa n'umubare w'abantu bapimwe, ubuziranenge bw'ubuvuzi, ubuvuzi buboneka, igihe cy'uburwayi, imibare y'abantu nk'imyaka, igitsina, n'ubuzima muri rusange.
Nk'uko imibare ya Kaminuza ya Johns Hopkins ibigaragaza, igipimo cy'urupfu ugereranyije n'ubwandu ni 6.0% (97,039/1,617,204) ku ya 10 Mata 2020.
