Ibipimo biri hejuru byemezwa n'ibyavuye mu igerageza rya mbere rya COVID-19 mu Budage, kandi ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bipimo by'ibanze ni bwo buvuga ko abantu bapfa.
OMS ivuga ko iki cyorezo cyugarije isi yose gishobora gukingirwa.
Igihe indwara itangiriye n'igihe ishobora kumara ntibiramenyekana kandi bishobora gutandukana bitewe n'akarere.
Maciej Boni wo muri kaminuza ya leta ya Pennsylvania, yaravuze ati "iyo indwara zandura zidakumiriwe, zigenda zikura, zikagenda zigabanuka.
Ariko kandi, nta muntu ushobora kumenya igihe kizaza".
Umujyanama wa Leta y'Ubushinwa, Zhong Nanshan, yavuze ko "bishobora kuba byarangiye ku wa Gatandatu" mu gihe ibihugu byose byashishikarizwa gukurikiza inama za OMS zo guhashya ikwirakwira ry'iyi virusi.
Ku ya 17 Werurwe, Adam Kucharski wo mu ishuri ry'isuku n'ubuvuzi bw'ikirere i Londres yavuze ko SARS-CoV-2 "izakomeza gukwirakwira, wenda mu mwaka umwe cyangwa ibiri".
Dukurikije ubushakashatsi bwakozwe na Kaminuza ya Imperial, bwakozwe na Neil Ferguson, kwifata no gukurikiza izindi ngamba bizakenerwa "kugeza igihe urukingo ruzaba rubonetse (hashobora gushira amezi 18 cyangwa arenga)".
William Schaffner wo muri Kaminuza ya Vanderbilt yagize ati "Ntekereza ko virusi ya coronavirusi ishobora guhinduka indwara y'igihe gito igaruka buri mwaka kubera ko ikwirakwira vuba".
Ingaruka z'uko kugaruka bizaterwa n'ubwoko bw'ibinyamushongo by'inyamaswa n'ubwoko bwayo.
Ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 bishobora kuba bidasanzwe kandi abantu barwaye bashobora kutagira ibimenyetso.
Ibimenyetso bibiri by'ibanze ni umuriro mwinshi (88%) n'igifu cyumye (68%).
Ibimenyetso bidakunze kugaragara ni nko guhumeka nabi, guhumeka nabi, guhumeka nabi, kubabara mu ngingo, kuribwa mu ijosi, umutwe, guhumeka nabi, kwitsamura, guhumeka amaraso (hemoptysis), guhinda umushyitsi cyangwa se kurwara ibicurane. OMS ivuga ko umuntu umwe kuri batandatu arwara indwara idakira kandi ko ahumeka nabi.
Ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) kivuga ko ibimenyetso by'ihungabana ari: guhumeka nabi, kubabara mu gatuza, kumva umunaniro, kugorwa no kugenda, no guhumeka mu maso cyangwa mu kanwa; ibimenyetso nk'ibyo bisaba ubuvuzi bwihutirwa.
Abarwayi bamwe bashobora kutagira ibimenyetso, ariko iyo basuzumwe bakemeza ko barwaye, abashakashatsi batanga inama ko abantu bahuye n'abarwayi bagombye gukurikiranwa cyane kugira ngo barebe ko nta bwandu bafite.
Leta y'Ubushinwa ivuga ko umubare w'abanduye uturuka ku bantu bake ugera kuri 44%.
Igihe cyo kugaragaza ibimenyetso (igihe kuva umuntu yanduye kugeza ibimenyetso bitangiye kugaragara) akenshi ni umunsi umwe kugeza ku minsi 14; akenshi ni iminsi itanu. Mu rugero rw'ibipimo bidashidikanywaho, imibare y'abantu banduye COVID-19 batashoboraga gukingira yagereranyaga 30% mu ntangiriro, hanyuma ikaza kugabanuka ikajya kuri 15%.
Hari ibintu byinshi bitarasobanuka neza ku birebana n'uko indwara zikwirakwira.
Bivugwa ko iyi ndwara yandura binyuze mu guhura n'abantu barwaye ndetse no gukorakora ibisebe byanduzwa no gukorora, kwitsamura cyangwa kuvuga; kandi ubwandu buba hagati ya metero 1 na 2 (metero 3 na 6).
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko iyo umuntu ahoshe atambaye akanwa, ashobora kugira igipimo cy'ubuhagarike kiri hagati ya metero 4,5 na metero 8.2.
Hari abavuga ko virusi ishobora no gukwirakwira binyuze mu mazi y'umwuka, ashobora guturuka mu kanwa, cyangwa se mu gihe umuntu arimo avuga, nubwo ubusanzwe nta virusi igenda mu mwuka.
Iyo urumogi rwinjiye mu kanwa cyangwa mu mazuru y'abantu bari hafi aho, cyangwa se rukinjira mu bihaha.
Hari imiti, urugero nko gutera mu nda no gutera mu mutima (CPR), ishobora gutuma mu mwuka w'umubiri habaho imyanda ituma umuntu atakaza umwuka.
Nanone ushobora kwandura iyo ukoreye ku kintu cyose kirimo mikorobe, mu maso, mu ngingo no mu kanwa.
Birumvikana ko hari ubwoba bw'uko ishobora gukwirakwira mu bibi, ubwo bwigomeke bukaba bufatwa nk'aho bufite imbaraga nke.
Leta y'Ubushinwa yanze ko SARS-CoV-2 ishobora gukwirakwira cyane. Virusi ikwirakwira cyane mu minsi itatu ya mbere y'igiteranyo cy'ibimenyetso, ariko ikwirakwira mbere y'ibimenyetso ndetse no mu byiciro bya nyuma by'ubwandu.
Abantu basuzumwa hashize iminsi itatu bataragaragaza ibimenyetso by'ubwandu, ibyo bikaba bigaragaza ko bashobora kwandura nubwo batagaragaza ibimenyetso bikomeye.
Hari raporo nke z'abarwayi bemejwe ko nta bimenyetso bagaragaza, ariko ikwirakwizwa ry'agakoko gatera SIDA riturutse ku bantu batagaragaza ibimenyetso ryagaragaye mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe mu gukurikirana guhura kw'abarwayi n'abandi bantu.
Ikigo cy'u Burayi gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (ECDC) kivuga ko nubwo nta wuzi neza uko iyi ndwara yandura, ubusanzwe umuntu umwe yandura abantu babiri cyangwa batatu.
Muri rusange, basanze iyo mikorobe imaze iminsi itatu iri ku bikoresho bya plastiki (polypropylene) n'ibikoresho by'ubushyuhe (cylindres) bya dogere 304, umunsi umwe iri ku ikarito, indi amasaha ane iri ku mpapuro.
Ariko kandi, ibi biratandukanye bitewe n'aho umwuka uri n'ubushyuhe. Amatungo n'amatungo na yo yasuzumwe asangwamo COVID-19.
Nta bimenyetso bifatika bigaragaza ko inyamaswa zishobora kwanduza abantu, nubwo abayobozi bo mu Bwongereza batanga inama yo gukaraba intoki nyuma yo gukora ku nyamaswa, nko gukora ku bintu byakozwe n'abantu bakekwaho uburwayi.
Indwara y'uburwayi idasanzwe ifata umwuka (Severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2)) ni virusi itaramenyekana, yagaragaye bwa mbere mu bantu batatu barwaye indwara y'uburwayi buteye ubukana yabonetse i Wuhan.
Ibimenyetso byose bya SARS-CoV-2 bitamenyekanye mbere byabonetse muri koronavirusi zisa n'imvura. Hanze y'umubiri wa muntu, virusi yica isabune ikoreshwa mu rugo, isabune yica uruhu rw'umubiri. SARS-CoV-2 isa cyane na SARS-CoV ya mbere.
Abantu benshi batekereza ko iyo ndwara yavuye mu nyamaswa igatangira kugaragara mu bantu.
