Abanyeshuri b'Abashinwa biga muri kaminuza zo muri Amerika bifatanyije mu bikorwa by'ubutabazi mu bice by'u Bushinwa byibasiwe cyane n'icyorezo, aho ikigo cyo muri Chicago cyohereje udupfukamunwa tw'ubwoko bwa N95 tugera ku 50,000 mu bitaro bya Hubei ku ya 30 Mutarama. Ikigo gishinzwe ubutabazi Direct Relief na FedEx byohereje udupfukamunwa 200,000 n'ibindi bikoresho birimo amakaramu n'amabati mu ndege y'ubutabazi ku bitaro bya Wuhan Union ku ya 30 Mutarama.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Bill na Melinda Gates batangaje inkunga ya miliyoni 100 z'amadolari ya Amerika ku kigo cy'isi cyita ku buzima OMS, kugira ngo gikore ubushakashatsi ku rukingo no kuvura no kurinda "abantu bafite ibibazo muri Afurika no muri Aziya y'Amajyepfo".
Interaksyon yatangaje ko leta y'Ubushinwa yatanze udupfukamunwa 200,000 muri Filipine ku ya 6 Gashyantare nyuma y'aho umujyanama Richard Gordon yohereje udupfukamunwa miliyoni 3.16 i Wuhan.
Ku ya 19 Gashyantare, Croix Rouge ya Singapour yatangaje ko igiye kohereza imfashanyo ya miliyoni $2.26 mu Bushinwa.
Ubuyapani bwatanze udupfukamunwa miliyoni imwe muri Wuhan, Turukiya yatanze ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, Uburusiya bwohereje toni 13 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi muri Wuhan, Malaysia yatangaje ko yatanze uturindantoki miliyoni 18 mu Bushinwa, Ubudage bwatanze ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi birimo amasuti 10,000 ya Hazmat, Amerika yatanze toni 17.8 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa kandi yizeza ko izatanga miliyoni 100 z'amadolari y'Amerika mu gufasha ibihugu byazahajwe n'icyorezo.
Mu kwezi kwa gatatu, Ubushinwa, Chuba n'Uburusiya byohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'inzobere mu gufasha u Butaliyani ku cyorezo cya coronavirus.
Umucuruzi Jack Ma yohereje ibikoresho byo gupima miliyoni 1.1, udupfukamunwa miliyoni 6, n'inkingo 60,000 muri Addis Ababa, Ethiopia, ku biro by'Umuryango wa Afurika Yunze Ubumwe.
Nyuma yaho yoherereje Panama ibikoresho byo gupima 5.000, udupfukamunwa 100.000 n'imashini 5 zo gutera mu nda.
Ma kandi yatanze ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi muri Canada. Ubuholandi, Espagne, Turukiya, Georgia na Repubulika ya Tchèque bitotombeye indwara ya kanseri n'ibikoresho byo gupima byakozwe mu Bushinwa.
Urugero, Espagne yahagaritse ibipimo bya koronavirusi 58.000 byakozwe mu Bushinwa ariko bikaba byari bifite ubuziranenge bwa 30% gusa, mu gihe Ubuholandi bwahagaritse inkingo 600.000 z'Abashinwa zishwe.
U Bubiligi bwashenye udupfukamunwa 100.000 tutari tugikenewe, bumvaga ko twavuye mu Bushinwa, ariko mu by'ukuri tukaba twaraturutse muri Kolombiya.
Ku rundi ruhande, inkunga y'Ubushinwa yakiriwe neza mu bice bya Amerika y'Amajyepfo na Afurika. Ku ya 2 Mata, Banki y'Isi yatangije inkunga yihutirwa ku bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere.
OMS yashimye imbaraga Ubushinwa bwashyizeho mu kurwanya indwara.
OMS yagaragaje itandukaniro hagati y'icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2002 na 2004, ubwo abategetsi b'Ubushinwa bahatiwe guhisha amabanga yabangamiye ibikorwa byo kwirinda no kurwanya, n'ikibazo cy'ubu ubwo leta nkuru "ihora iburira abaturage kwirinda icyorezo mu gihe bitegura iminsi mikuru y'umwaka mushya wa Lunar".
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, mu gusubiza icyemezo cy'abayobozi ba leta cyo guhagarika ingendo mu mujyi wa Wuhan, Gauden Galea, uhagarariye OMS yavuze ko "nubwo OMS atari yo yafashe icyemezo", "ari igikorwa cyiza kandi kigaragaza ko yiyemeje kurwanya iki cyorezo mu karere gashishikaje cyane" kandi ko "bitigeze bibaho mu mateka y'ubuvuzi". Ku ya 30 Mutarama, ubwo ubwandu bw'umuntu ku wundi bwari bwemejwe hanze y'Ubushinwa kandi umubare w'abanduye ukomeje kwiyongera mu bindi bihugu, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari ikibazo cy'ubuzima rusange ku isi (Public Health Emergency of International Concern (PHEIC), nk'uko byari bisanzwe kuva icyorezo cya kabiri cy'ibicurane cyatangira kugaragara mu 2009.
Tedros Adhanom, umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, yavuze ko PHEIC yatewe n'uko "ikwirakwira mu bihugu bikennye n'ibifite ubukungu buciriritse, aho usanga nta buvuzi buhagije buhari.
Mu gusubiza ikibazo cy'ingendo za leta, Tedros yavuze ko "nta mpamvu yo guhagarika ingendo n'ubucuruzi ku isi" kandi ko "WHO idashyigikira ko ingendo n'ubucuruzi bigabanywa".
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, OMS yasabye isi yose gutanga miliyoni 675 z'amadolari y'Amerika mu rwego rwo kwitegura mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, ivuga ko hakenewe ubufasha bwihutirwa mu bihugu "bitagira uburyo bwo gupima abantu banduye, mu gihe habayeho icyorezo".
Tedros yatangaje kandi ko "imbaraga zacu zingana n'aho turi intege nke cyane" kandi asaba abantu ku isi yose "kubiba uyu munsi cyangwa kwishyura ejo".Ku ya 11 Gashyantare, OMS mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru yatangaje COVID-19 nk'izina ry'icyorezo.
Kuri uwo munsi, Tedros yavuze ko Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye António Guterres yemeye gutanga "imbaraga zose z'Umuryango w'Abibumbye mu kurwanya indwara".
Itsinda rya ONU rishinzwe kurwanya ibiza ryashyizweho, mu rwego rwo guhuza ibikorwa by'Umuryango w'Abibumbye, nk'uko OMS ibivuga, bizafasha "kwita ku buzima nk'uko izindi nzego z'ubuzima ziteranya ubumenyi bwazo mu gufasha mu bibazo by'imibereho myiza y'abantu, ubukungu n'iterambere muri iki gihe cy'icyorezo".
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare, itsinda ry'abafatanyabikorwa ryateguwe na OMS mu Bushinwa ryashyizweho kugira ngo ritange impuguke zo ku isi no muri OMS mu Bushinwa kugira ngo zifashe mu guhangana n'ibibazo by'imbere mu gihugu no gusuzuma "ubukana n'ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo" binyuze mu gutegura amahugurwa n'inama n'inzego z'ibanze z'igihugu no gusura uturere kugira ngo basuzume "ibisubizo by'ibikorwa ku rwego rw'intara n'intara, harimo n'imijyi n'imidugudu". Ku ya 25 Gashyantare, OMS yatangaje ko "isi ikeneye gukora byinshi kurushaho mu kwitegura coronavirus ishobora kuba ikibazo cy'isi yose", kandi ko nubwo ibihugu byari byaravuze ko ari icyorezo, byari bikwiye kuba "icyorezo cy'isi yose".
Ku cyorezo cyatangiye muri Irani, OMS yohereje Itsinda ry'Ibikorwa Rihuriweho (Joint Mission Team) kugira ngo rigenzure uko ibintu byifashe.Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, abayobozi ba OMS bavuze ko icyiciro cyo gusuzuma icyorezo cya coronavirus ku isi cyose cyagombaga kuzamurwa kikava ku cyiciro cya "cy'indwara ikomeye" kikajya ku cyiciro cya "cy'indwara ikomeye cyane", kikaba ari cyo cyiciro cya mbere cyo gusuzuma icyorezo.
Mike Ryan, umuyobozi wa gahunda y'ubutabazi bw'ibanze bwa OMS, yatanze umuburo agira ati "iyi ni yo ntambwe buri butegetsi bwose ku isi bwagombye gutera: Mukanguke.
Iyi virusi ishobora kuba iri mu nzira kandi mugomba kuba mwiteguye", akaba yaburiye ko gushyiraho ingamba z'ingirakamaro zo kuyirwanya bishobora gufasha isi kwirinda "ikibazo gikomeye kurushaho".
Ryan yakomeje avuga ko amakuru y'ubu adatuma abayobozi b'ubuzima batangaza ko iki cyorezo cyakwirakwiriye ku isi hose, avuga ko gutangaza bene ibyo byaba bivuze ko "twemera ko buri muntu wese ku isi ashobora kwandura".
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, OMS yatangaje ko coronavirus ari icyorezo ku isi.
Umuyobozi Mukuru wa OMS yavuze ko "yahangayikishijwe cyane n'umuvuduko wa virusi n'ubukana bwayo, n'ukuntu nta kintu kinini cyakozwe". OMS iri mu byago bikomeye kubera ko igaragara ko idakora cyane mu guhangana n'iki cyorezo, harimo no gutinda gutangaza ko ari ikibazo cy'ubuzima gikeneye kwitabwaho byihutirwa no kucyitirira isi yose.
Ibi bitero by'ibyihebe byasabye umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS Tedros Adhanom kwegura, ubwo iyi gahunda yasinywaga n'abantu 733.000 ku itariki ya 6 Mata.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, impuguke z'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ku burenganzira bwa muntu zasabye ko uburenganzira bwa muntu bwubahirizwa mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Iryo tsinda ry'impuguke ryavuze ko abantu bose bafite uburenganzira bwo kwivuza kandi ko ari inshingano ya leta.
Iri tsinda ryashimangiye ko kubura ibikoresho cyangwa ubwisungane mu kwivuza bitagomba gufatwa nk'impamvu yo kutorohereza abantu bamwe na bamwe.
Abahanga bagaragaje ko buri muntu afite uburenganzira ku buzima, harimo abamugaye, abantu bake, abageze mu za bukuru, abari mu nkambi z'impunzi, abatagira aho baba, abari mu mimerere mibi, imfungwa, impunzi n'abandi bose bakeneye ubufasha bwa leta.
Ibigo bya leta ku isi yose birimo gusubiza ibibazo by'ubukungu n'imibereho ya muntu byatewe na COVID-19.
Ni irihe shyirahamwe ry'ubufatanye mu bukungu n'iterambere ryashyizeho uburyo bwo gutanga amakuru ku gihe kandi arambuye ku bikorwa byashyizweho mu bihugu byo ku isi, hamwe n'ibitekerezo n'ibitekerezo.
Kuva ku ngamba zo gukomeza ubuvuzi n'ubukungu ku isi kugeza ku guhangana n'ingaruka z'ikumira n'ibihano byo guhagarika ingendo, gahunda nshya irimo Country Policy Tracker, kandi igamije gufasha ibihugu kwiga ku mishyikirano no guhuza imbaraga ku isi yose mu guhangana n'ikibazo cya coronavirus.
Leta y'Ubushinwa yanenze cyane Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, Minisitiri w'Intebe w'Ubwongereza Michael Gove, n'umuhungu wa Perezida wa Burezili Jair Bolsonaro witwa Eduardo Bolsonaro kubera uburyo bakemuye iki cyorezo cyatangiriye mu Ntara ya Hubei yo mu Bushinwa.
Abayobozi benshi bo mu rwego rw'intara mu ishyaka ry'Abakomunisiti b'Ubushinwa (CPC) birukanywe kubera uburyo bakiriye gahunda yo gushyira abantu mu kato mu Bushinwa rwagati, ikimenyetso cy'uko badashimishijwe n'uburyo abayobozi bakemura indwara muri utwo turere.
Bamwe mu basesenguzi batekereza ko iki gikorwa cyakozwe mu rwego rwo guhashya umunyabanga mukuru w'ishyaka rya gikomunisiti ry'Ubushinwa Xi Jinping, kubera uburakari bw'abantu kubera icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Bamwe mu bayobozi b'Ubushinwa, barimo Zhao Lijian, bahakanye igitekerezo cya mbere cy'uko coronavirus yatangiriye i Wuhan, bashyigikira igitekerezo cy'ubuvugizi cy'uko COVID-19 yatangiriye muri Amerika cyangwa mu Butaliyani.
Ubuyobozi bwa Donald Trump muri Amerika buvuga ko coronavirus ari "Virus y'Ubushinwa" cyangwa "Virus ya Wuhan" bavuga ko "Ubushinwa bwatsinzwe butuma bakora virusi ubu yabaye ikibazo cy'isi yose", ibyo bikaba byashyizwe ku ruhande na bamwe bavuga ko ari ivangura "biturutse ku kunanirwa kw'ubuyobozi mu kurwanya iki cyorezo".
Daily Beast yabonye amakuru ya leta ya Amerika yerekana amayeri y'itumanaho y'inama y'umutekano w'igihugu, avuga ko "byose ari ibya Ubushinwa.
Twabwiwe kugerageza gutangaza amakuru mu buryo bwose bushoboka, harimo inama n'amatangazo y'abanyamakuru no kugaragara kuri televiziyo".Ibinyamakuru nka Politico, Foreign Policy na Bloomberg byatangaje ko ibikorwa by'Ubushinwa byo gufasha ibihugu byugarijwe n'icyorezo ari kimwe mu bikorwa by'ubucuruzi by'isi.
Umuyobozi ushinzwe politiki y'amahanga muri EU Josep Borrell yaburiye ko hari " politiki y'amahanga irimo intambara y'ubwisanzure n' 'politiki y'ubwikunde'".
Borrell yakomeje avuga ko "Ubushinwa buhatanira kugaragaza ko butandukanye na Amerika, ko bufite inshingano kandi ko bufite icyizere".
Ubushinwa bwasabye kandi Amerika kugura sima muri Syria, Venezuela na Iran, mu gihe bwo bukomeje kohereza imfashanyo muri ibyo bihugu.
Impano ya Jack Ma y'udupfukamunwa 100,000 yagenewe Cuba yahagaritswe n'ibiro bya Amerika ku ya 3 Mata.
Nanone kandi, abayobozi bo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika bashinjwaga ko bari barafashe imfashanyo zari zatanzwe n'ibindi bihugu, maze bakazihagarika.
Hari kandi impaka z'ubwandu bw'ibicurane hagati y'ibindi bihugu, nk'u Budage, Otirishiya n'u Busuwisi; na Repubulika ya Tchèque n'u Butaliyani.
Ikindi kandi, Turukiya yatanze ibikoresho bifashisha guhumeka bibarirwa mu magana byo kohereza muri Esipanye.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, leta y'Ubutaliyani yanenze Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi ku kuba utari bufatanye n'Ubutaliyani mu guhangana na coronavirus.
Maurizio Massari, uhagarariye u Butaliyani mu muryango w'ibihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi, yaravuze ati "U Bushinwa ni bwo bwonyine bwabashishikaje.
Uko byaba biri kose, icyo si ikimenyetso cyiza cy'uko u Burayi bufatanyije".
Ku itariki ya 22 Werurwe, nyuma yo kuvugana kuri telefoni na Minisitiri w'Intebe w'u Butaliyani Giuseppe Conte, Perezida w'u Burusiya Vladimir Putin yateganyije ko ingabo z'u Burusiya zohereza abaganga b'abasirikare, imodoka zitwara imiti n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Butaliyani.
Ikinyamakuru cyo mu Butaliyani cyitwa La Stampa cyerekeje ku "munyapolitiki ukomeye" utari ushyigikiwe, kivuga ko 80 ku ijana by'ubufasha bw'u Burusiya "nta cyo bwari bumaze cyangwa nta cyo bwari bumaze ku Butaliyani".
Uwo munyapolitiki yasabye u Burusiya gukina "poritiki" y'ubushyamirane.
Minisitiri w'Intebe wa Lombardy, Attilio Fontana, na Minisitiri w'Ububanyi n'Amahanga w'u Butaliyani, Luigi Di Maio, na bo bashimye cyane iyo nkuru.
Uburusiya kandi bwohereje indege y'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi muri Amerika.
Umuvugizi wa Kremlin witwa Dmitry Peskov, yavuze ko [Putin] "yifuza ko abaganga bo muri Amerika bazamwishyura igihe cyose azaba akeneye ubufasha".
Porogaramu ya NATO "Defender 2020" mu Budage, Polonye, n'ibihugu bya Baltic, gahunda ikomeye cyane ya gisirikare ya NATO kuva intambara y'ubutita irangiye, izaba mu buryo buciriritse.
Kate Hudson, umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyirahamwe ryita ku kurwanya intwaro za kirimbuzi, yanenze gahunda ya Defender 2020 agira ati "mu gihe cy'ibibazo by'ubuzima biriho, ubuzima bw'abasirikare ba Amerika n'ibihugu byinshi by'i Burayi hamwe n'abaturage b'ibihugu bakoreramo buri mu kaga".
Perezida wa Irani Hassan Rouhani yandikiye abayobozi b'isi mu ibaruwa yo gusaba ubufasha ku ya 14 Werurwe 2020, avuga ko igihugu cye kizahura n'ibibazo mu guhangana n'icyorezo cy'ibiyobyabwenge ku isoko mpuzamahanga bitewe n'ibihano by'Amerika kuri Iran. Iki cyorezo cyongereye imbaraga ku buryo Amerika ikoresha politiki z'imibereho myiza zisanzwe zisanzwe mu bihugu bikize, zirimo kwivuza kuri bose, kwita ku bana bose, ikiruhuko gihenze, no gushora imari nyinshi mu bikorwa by'imibereho myiza ya bose.
Abakurikiranira hafi ibya politiki bavuze ko bishobora kugira ingaruka ku bushobozi bwa Donald Trump bwo kongera gutorerwa kuyobora u Buyapani mu matora ya Perezida wa Amerika yo mu 2020.
