Hakoreshejwe uburyo bwa Real-time reverse transcription polymerase chain reaction (rRT-PCR) ubu bushakashatsi bushobora gukorwa ku bipimo by'umwanda byavanywe mu buryo butandukanye, harimo no gutera mu mazuru no mu mazuru cyangwa ibipimo by'umwanda.
