Ingirabuzima fatizo ya Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) ni ingirabuzima fatizo ifata ku mubiri (ku mubiri w'ingirabuzima fatizo) ikora ku mikaya, ku mitsi, ku mutima, ku mpyiko no mu mara.
ACE2 ihagarika ingufu za angiotensin-converting enzyme (ACE) igabanya ingano ya angiotensin-II mu kongera Ang (((1-7) ikayigira umuti ushobora gukoreshwa mu kurwanya indwara z'umutima. ACE2 ikora nk'intangiriro yo kurwanya coronavirus zimwe na zimwe.
Muri rusange, abantu bakunze kwita ako gace ADN, ACE2.
Ingirabuzima fatizo ya Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 ni ingirabuzima fatizo ya zinc, ikaba iboneka ku mibiri y'utugingo ngengabuzima tw'amaraso n'utundi.
Poroteyine ya ACE2 igizwe n'uruziga rwa N-terminal peptidase M2 na C-terminal collectrin renal amino acid transporter domain.
ACE2 inyura mu ruhu rw'umubiri rimwe, ibice byayo by'ingenzi bikagaragara ku gice cy'inyuma cy'umubiri mu ngingo n'indi mibiri.
Uruhande rw'inyuma rwa ACE2 ruva ku ruhu rukagenda rujyanwa mu kindi gice cy'umubiri cyitwa sheddase, maze poroteyine z'umwimerere zigatangira kujyanwa mu maraso, nyuma zigasubirana amazi.
ACE2 iboneka mu bice byinshi by'umubiri: ACE2 ifata ku mubiri cyane cyane ku ngirabuzima fatizo z'ubwonko z'ubwoko bwa II ku nkuta z'ibihaha, ku nkingo z'amaraso, ku mitsi n'utugingo ngengabuzima tw'amaraso, no ku ngirabuzima fatizo z'imyakura mu bice byinshi by'umubiri.
ACE2 mRNA kandi iboneka mu gice cy'ubwonko, mu gice cy'inyuma cy'umubiri, mu gice cy'ubwonko cyitwa hypothalamus no mu gice cy'ubwonko cyitwa cortex.
Icy'ingenzi ACE2 ikora ni ukugabanya ACE
ACE ifata ingirabuzima fatizo ya angiotensin I ikayigira ingirabuzima fatizo ya angiotensin II.
ACE2 noneho ifata amino acide phenylalanine yo mu gice cy'umushongi wa karuboni (carboxyl-terminal amino acid phenylalanine) iva muri angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) ikayivamo angiotensin yo mu gice cy'umushinge wa arteri (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 ishobora no kwibanda ku nkingo zitandukanye zirimo [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A na ghrelin.
ACE2 kandi igenzura uburyo bwo gutwara amino acide itagira aho ihuriye na SLC6A19 kandi bivugwa ko ari yo ituma indwara ya Hartnup ibaho.
Kubera ko poroteyine itwara virusi mu ruhu, ACE2 ikora nk'irembo ry'ingenzi ry'ubudahangarwa bwa virusi zimwe na zimwe za corona, harimo HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virusi itera SARS); na SARS-CoV-2 (virusi itera COVID-19).
By'umwihariko, guhuza poroteyine ya S1 ya SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV2 ku gice cy'ingenzi cya ACE2 ku gice cy'umubiri bituma virusi n'indwara biva mu cyumba cyazo bigasubira mu nkingi z'ingirabuzimafatizo.
Ubu buryo bwo kwinjira kandi bukenera ko poroteyine S igabanywa na TMPRSS2 ya serine protease, ubu ikoreshwa mu kwivuza. Ibi byatumye bamwe batekereza ko kugabanya ACE2 mu ngirabuzimafatizo, bishobora gufasha kurwanya ubwandu.
Ariko, inzego zitandukanye z'ubuvuzi n'iz'ubugenzuzi zashyigikiye gukomeza gukoresha ACE inhibitor izwi cyane hamwe n'ubuvuzi bwa ARB.
