Ubundi buryo bworoshye bwo gukoresha Bluetooth ni ugushyira telefoni yawe kuri telefone iri hafi
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple batangaje ko bagiye gufatanya gushyigikira porogaramu ya Bluetooth kuri Android na iOS mu buryo butaziguye mu bikoresho byabo.
Mu Bushinwa, leta y'Ubushinwa ifatanyije na Alipau, bashyizeho porogaramu ituma abaturage bayo bashobora gupima niba barigeze guhura n'abantu bafite COVID-19.
Ikoreshwa mu mijyi isaga 200 yo mu Bushinwa, muri Singapore hakoreshwa porogaramu yitwa TraceTogether.
Porogaramu yakozwe n'abakozi ba IT bo muri ako gace, kandi yashyizwe ahagaragara nk'ifungurwa rusange kandi izatangwa na leta. Macedonia ya Ruguru yatangije porogaramu ya Bluetooth "StopKorona!", kugirango ikurikirane abitabiriye hamwe n'abantu bakekwaho uburwayi kandi ihite yohereza amakuru ku barwayi n'abategetsi.
Porogaramu yakozwe na Minisiteri y'Itumanaho n'Ikoranabuhanga hamwe na Minisiteri y'Ubuzima.
Kugeza ku ya 14 Mata 2020, porogaramu iracyari kugenzurwa na Google Play Store na Apple App Store.
Ku ya 12 Mata, leta yatangaje ko porogaramu yo gukurikirana abanduye iri mu cyiciro cya nyuma cy'ibikorwa, kandi ko izaba itangiye gukora mu byumweru bike. Porogaramu nk'iyo iri gutegurwa muri Irilande, u Bufaransa ("StopCovid").
Australia na Nouvelle Zelande birimo gusuzuma porogaramu ya TraceTogether ya Singapore hamwe na BlueTrace protocol.Uburusiya burateganya gushyiraho porogaramu ya geofencing ku barwayi ba COVID-19 baba i Moscou, bagamije kwirinda kuva mu rugo.
Ross Anderson, umwarimu wigisha iby'ubwubatsi bw'umutekano muri Kaminuza ya Cambridge, yavuze ko hari ibibazo bishobora kuvuka mu mikorere ishingiye kuri porogaramu, harimo no gutekereza ko ikora neza cyangwa ko idashobora gukora neza iyo porogaramu ikoreshwa mu ibaruramari.
Mu rwego rwo guhangana n'ibibazo by'ibikorwa bya coronavirus byangiza cyangwa byangiza, Apple yashyizeho imipaka ku bigo bishobora gushyiraho porogaramu zijyanye na coronavirus muri App Store, yemera gusa ibigo cyangwa ibigo byemewe.
Google na Amazon na byo byashyizeho amategeko amwe.
Abashyigikira ibanga bagaragaje impungenge ku ngaruka zo gukurikirana abakoresha porogaramu nyinshi za coronavirus, cyane cyane kwibaza niba uburyo bwo gukurikirana bwakozwe mu buryo bworoshye buzakurwaho mugihe icyorezo kirangiye.
