Tariki ya 6 Mata 2020, ibitaramo byari bitaratangira.
Gukurikirana abakorana n'umurwayi ni gahunda iteguwe neza, hakoreshejwe ubushakashatsi bwinshi kuva mu 2013. Ku ya 7 Mata 2020, amatsinda y'abahanga atandukanye arimo gukora ku kunoza uburyo bw'ibanga, nko gukoresha Bluetooth Low Energy (BLE) kumenya aho ukoresha ukoresheje izindi terefone.
Ubusanzwe, PEPP-PT ni uburyo bwo guhuza abantu bufite uburyo butandukanye, kandi ntibukurikiza amategeko amwe. Amategeko atandukanye arimo Decentralized Privacy-Preserving Proximity Tracing (DP-PPT/DP-3T), Imibare y'igihe gito yo guhura (TCN, cyangwa Contact Event Numbers, CEN), Privacy Sensitive Protocols na Mechanisms for Mobile Contact Tracing (PACT) n'ibindi.
Muri ayo mategeko, nta kintu na kimwe cy'ingenzi kigomba gukurwa mu cyuma, kandi buri kintu cyose cy'ingenzi kigomba gukorwa.
Itsinda rya Twekisize muri MIT Media Lab ryatangije SafePaths, uburyo bwitwa gukoresha ubuhanga bwo kugenzura no gukoresha imbuga za interineti mu gukurikirana ikwirakwira rya COVID-19.
Bishingiye ku bushakashatsi bwakozwe na raporo "Apps Gone Rogue: Kurinda ubuzima bwite mu gihe cy'icyorezo" yasohotse muri Werurwe 2020. Ubundi buryo buhuje n'ubwo ni urubuga rwa SafeTrace rwakozwe na Enigma MPC, ikigo cy'ikoranabuhanga ry'ibanga kandi cyahoze gikorera muri MIT Media Lab.
SafeTrace ikora ikoranabuhanga ridafite ibyago rifasha abakoresha gusangira amakuru y'ibanga yerekeye aho bari n'ubuzima bwabo n'abandi bakoresha n'abayobozi, nta guhungabanya ubuzima bwite.
Ku ya 5 Mata 2020, ishyirahamwe mpuzamahanga TCN Coalition ryatangijwe n'amashyirahamwe akoresha uburyo bumwe n'amategeko amwe, hagamijwe kugabanya umubare w'amashyirahamwe, kandi gusangira hamwe gukora porogaramu zo gukurikirana no kohereza ubutumwa, ikintu cy'ingenzi mu gutuma abantu benshi bashobora kubikora.
Ku ya 9 Mata 2020, guverinoma ya Singapore yatangaje ko ikoresha BlueTrace protocol ikoreshwa na porogaramu ya leta yayo.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple, ibigo by'ubucuruzi bigenzura porogaramu za Android na iOS, byatangaje uburyo bwo gukurikirana abakora ku mbuga nkoranyambaga, bavuga ko buzakomeza ubuzima bwite, bushingiye ku guhuza ikoranabuhanga rya Bluetooth Low Energy n'ibanga ryanditse.
Nanone kandi, basohoye amakuru y'ikoranabuhanga rihambaye cyane rikoreshwa mu gukora ibirungo.
Nk'uko Apple na Google babivuga, urubuga rwiteganyijwe gutangwa mu byiciro bitatu:
