Ni kimwe mu bikorwa bya siyansi byo gukora imiti ya COVID-19 idafite ubwandu kandi ikora neza.
Mu bindi bikorwa by'ubushakashatsi birimo gukora urukingo rwa COVID-19 no guterwa amaraso mu mubiri. SARS-CoV-2 ifite poroteyine zigera kuri 66 z'ubwoko butandukanye, buri bwoko bukaba bufite ahantu henshi hahuza ibinyamubiri.
Gusuzuma aho izo poroteyine zifatanya bifasha mu gukora imiti igabanya ubukana bwa poroteyine za COVID-19.
Poroteyine z'ingenzi SARS-CoV-2 yibasira ni protease isa na papain, RNA-dependent RNA polymerase, helicase, S protein, na ADP ribophosphatase.
Hussein A A, et al basuzumye ibintu byinshi birimo no gusuzuma uburyo bwo kuvura neza cyane bwasabwe kugira ngo byihutishe iterambere ry'imiti ikomeye ya SARS-CoV-2 mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe mbere yo gutangazwa mu bushakashatsi bw'ubuvuzi.
Chloroquine ni umuti uvura malariya kandi ukoreshwa mu kurwanya indwara z'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri.
